\toc1 God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim Samuel, An Ak…®nafarir Namba 2
\mt1 God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim Samuel, // An Ak…®nafarir Namba 2
\mt2 O
\mt1 2 Samuel
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam…®n eghaghaniba, da Samuel…®n Ak…®nafarir Namba 1…®n eghaghanim…®n g…®n, otivizir bizibagh eghari. Ak…®nafarir kamning faragha ak…®nafarir vam…®ran ike. Samuel…®n Ak…®nafarir Namba 2, a gumazir vam…®ra geghari, kar Atrivim Devit. Kamagh…®n, me g…®n an ogharaz…®, a ua baghav…®ra iti. Ak…®nafarir kam, a Devit atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n bizibagh eghari.
\ip God Atrivim Devit ko iti. Devit a gumazir gavgavim, a God gifongeghav…®ra ikia, egha uaghan Israelian gumazamizibagh ifonge. A n…®ghn…®zir bar gavgavim God…®n iti, ez…® Israelia bar a gifonge. Dughiar mabar, Devit uan inivaf…®zir agorogem…®n g…®n ghua, arazir kurar av…®rir maba uaghan dagh ami. Ez…® g…®n God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Natan, Devit…®n arazir kurabar an akaz…®, a uan arazir kurabar gun m…®kemegha navim g…®ra.
\ip Israelian damazim…®n, Devit bar ziar ekiam iti. Devit…®n dughiam…®n g…®n, os…®mt…®ziba Israelia bativima, me uam Atrivim Devit g…®n…®ghn…®si. Egha me kamagh…®n pamtem…®n n…®ghn…®si, me Devit…®n m…®n garir atrivir gavgavitam ik…®t…® deragham. Devit…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ko navim g…®razir arazim bang…®n, a Israelian tong…®n bar ziar ekiam ini.
\c 1
\ms1 Devit Israelian atrivim…®n oto
\mr (Sapta 1--9)
\s1 Devit Sol…®n ovevem…®n akam baraki
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n, Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua Amalekia ko m…®sogha itima, Atrivim Sol danganir igharazim…®n Filistiaba ko m…®soghava areme. Devit m…®dorozim…®n Amalekia ab…®nigha g…®vagha, me uamategha Siklak…®n nguibar ekiam…®n izegha aruer pumuning…®n iti. Dughiar kam…®n Atrivim Sol aremegha g…®fa, ez…® Devit tong fozir puvat…®.
\v 2 Ez…® namba 3…®n aruem…®n, gumazir igiar mam iza Siklak…®n oto. A iza uan os…®mt…®zim akakaghasa uan korotiam abigha beghneaziba uan dapanim gaghui. A Devit bagha ghugha uan tevimning ap…®righa guam nguazim…®n m…®tuagha, ziar ekiam Devit gan…®di. Gumazir kam Sol iti nagh…®n ikegha ize.
\v 3 Ez…® Devit an azara, ‚ÄúN…® managh…®ra ikegha izi?‚Äù
\p Ez…® gumazir igiam ghaze, ‚ÄúApaniba Israelia gas…®ghas…®zima, k…® en m…®dorozir gumaziba iti nagh…®n, me ategha ara n…® bagha izi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Devit an azara, ‚ÄúGa uaning, n…® m…®dorozim…®n otivizir bizibar gun na geghan.‚Äù
\p Ez…® gumazir igiam a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIsraelian m…®dorozir gumaziba m…®dorozim…®n arez…®, Filistiaba men gumazir av…®rim m…®soaghar…®ghiz…® me ariaghire, ez…® Atrivim Sol uan otarim Jonatan ko, aning uaghan areme.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Devit an azara, ‚ÄúN…® manmagh…®n Sol ko Jonatan…®n ovevem g…®fo?‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6-10 \xt 1 Samuel 31:1-6; 1 Eghaghaniba 10:1-6\x*Ez…® gumazir igiar kam ghaze, ‚ÄúK…®, Gilboan m…®ghs…®am…®n p…®n tughav ikia garima, Sol uan afuzim nguazim gasaragha gavgavim uab…® gan…®ga tughav iti. K…® garima, apaniba Sol…®n borogh…®n zui, kar karisba ko hoziabagh apiaghira m…®sozir m…®dorozir gumaziba.
\v 7 Ez…® Sol ragh…®r…®gha nan gara nan dia. Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄòGumazir ekiam, k…® kagh iti.‚Äô
\v 8 A kamagh…®n nan azara, ‚ÄòN…® nguibar manam…®n gumazim?‚Äô Ez…® k…® ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® Amalekian mav.‚Äô
\v 9 Ez…® a kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® na bagh zuam…®ra iz…®va bar na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeka. Nan apaniba bar puv…®ra na m…®soghez…®ma, nan damaziba nan s…®rima, k…® k…®ran oveghang…®n ovengam.‚Äô
\v 10 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, k…® an akam baregha an borogh…®n ghua a m…®soghez…® an areme. K…® kamagh…®n fo, a bar g…®fa, a nguazim gir…®gh bar aremegham. An aremegha g…®vaz…®, k…® an atrivibar dapanir asuam ko daveriam inigha, n…® bagha izi. Nan gumazir ekiam, aningra kara.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Devit akar kam baregha bar osemegha uan korotiam ab…®ki. Ez…® an m…®dorozir gumaziba uaghan kamagh…®ram ami.
\v 12 Me fo, Sol ko Jonatan ko Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ko Israelian gumazamizir igharaziba sara, me bar mogh…®ra m…®dorozir sababar ariaghire. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me bar men apangkuvigha osemegha azia, dagheba tagha ikia ghua guarat…®zim…®n tu.
\p 
\v 13 Egha Devit gumazir igiar kam kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúN…® nguibar manam…®n gumazim?‚Äù
\p Ez…® a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Amalekian mav, nan afeziam fom…®ra Amalekian nguazim ategha iza Israel…®n kantrin nguazim gapera.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Devit uam an azara, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n ami? N…® atrivim…®n m…®sogha tong atiatir puvat…®? Kar atrivir Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®sevezim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Egha Devit uan m…®dorozir gumazir mam…®n diaz…®, a izima a kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® gumazir kam m…®sueght…® an aremegh.‚Äù Ez…® Devit…®n m…®dorozir gumazim, m…®dorozir sabam…®n gumazir kam okez…® an areme.
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Devit, Amalekian gumazir kuar kam…®n gara ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® amizir os…®mt…®zim bang…®n n…® areme. N…® uab…® uab…®n gun m…®g…®a ghaze, K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®sevezir atrivim m…®soghez…®, an areme.‚Äù
\s1 Devit aziava Sol ko Jonatan bagha aghuimazir onger akam bange
\p 
\v 17 Egha Devit bar osemegha, Sol uan otarim Jonatan ko aning g…®n…®ghn…®gha aghuimazir ighiam bange.
\v 18 Devit akar gavgavim Judan gumazamizibagh an…®ga ghaze, me ighiar kam bangam. Ighiar kam…®n ziam, Barir Pim…®n Ighiam. Egha me a isa Jasar…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n an osiri. Devit kamagh…®n ighiar kam bati:\f + \fr 1:18 \ft Fofozir gumaziba ghaze, Jasar…®n Ak…®nafarir kam, a Israelian ak…®nafarir ghurir mam. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n ak…®nafarir kam bar ovenge, ez…® e fozir puvat…® akar manaba an ike. Josua God ko m…®geima an aruem gamiz…® an overiam…®n tughav itir dughiam…®n eghaghanim, a uaghan ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti. N…® Josua 10:12-13…®n gan.\f*
\b
\q1 
\v 19 ‚ÄúGumazir en faragha zuiba,
\q2 me Israelia en gumaziba,
\q3 me m…®ghs…®abagh is…®n ariaghire.
\q1 En m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba
\q2 ariaghiregha g…®fa.
\q1 
\v 20 Ia Get…®n nguibar ekiam ko Askelon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n tuavibar
\q2 bizir kam…®n gun m…®k…®man mark…®.
\q1 Filistian amiziba oregh
\q2 bar akuegham.
\q1 Eght…® God g…®fozir puvat…®zibar guiviba,
\q2 me navir am…®rizim inigh bar akuegham.
\b
\q1 
\v 21 ‚ÄúEn m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba
\q2 Gilboan m…®ghs…®abar ariaghire.
\q1 Ez…® m…®dorozir oraba
\q2 pura m…®ghs…®ar kabagh irav iti.
\q1 Ez…® Sol…®n oram uaghan pura iti,
\q2 ez…® me borem uam a gazuir puvat…®.
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® kamaghsua, amozim ko d…®magarim…®n ghuariam m…®ghs…®ar kam uam a giran mark…®.
\q2 Eght…® dagher aghuiba ua nguazir kam…®n aghungan kogham.
\b
\q1 
\v 22 ‚ÄúJonatan…®n barir pim a paza zuir puvat…®.
\q2 Ez…® Sol…®n m…®dorozir sabam pura itir puvat…®.
\q1 A m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavibav soghez…® me ariaghire,
\q2 ez…® apanibar ghuziba ko oviba bar a noke.
\q1 
\v 23 Gumazamiziba bar Sol ko Jonatan gifonge.
\q2 Aning gumazir bar aghuimning.
\q1 Aning zurara roroamning…®n m…®n uaning…®n poroghav ikia,
\q2 kamagh…®ra ikia ghuava areme.
\q1 Aning pamtem…®n uan apanibar ag…®nt…®si,
\q2 egha aning kuarazir isaba as…®zibar ag…®nt…®zir ivemarir arazim gafira.
\q1 Egha aning gavgavir ekiam ikia
\q2 laion…®n gavgavim gafira.
\b
\q1 
\v 24 ‚ÄúIa, Israelian amiziba, ia Sol bagh azirakabar amuva an aghuimazim…®n ik…®.
\q2 A korotiar aghevir aghuiba isa ia gan…®ngiz…® ia uari as…®ngi.
\q1 Dar iveziba bar p…®n iti.
\q2 A gol…®n adiarir aghuir guar av…®riba isa ia gan…®ngi.
\b
\q1 
\v 25 ‚ÄúM…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba m…®dorozim…®n ariaghire.
\q2 Ez…® Jonatan uaghan areme,
\q3 ez…® an kuam m…®ghs…®am…®n p…®n iti.
\q1 
\v 26 O Jonatan, nan roroam!
\q2 K…® bar n…®n apangkuvigha oseme.
\q1 K…® bar n…® gifonge,
\q2 ez…® n…® uaghan bar na gifonge.
\q1 N…® na gifongezir arazim, a bar gavgavigha, bar ekefe,
\q2 egha amiziba bar na gifongezir arazim, a bar men ifongiam gafira.
\q1 
\v 27 M…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba m…®dorozim…®n ariaghiregha g…®fa,
\q2 ez…® m…®dorozim gamir biziba da bar ikuvigha g…®fa.‚Äù
\c 2
\s1 Devit Judabar atrivim…®n oto
\p 
\v 1 Sol ko Jonatan…®n ovevem…®n g…®n, Devit kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azai, ‚ÄúK…® ti mang…®va Judan nguibar ekiatam dapiam, o puvat…®gham?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…®.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Devit ua kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúK…® mang…® nguibar ekiar manam dapiam?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…®va Hebron…®n nguibar ekiam…®n daperagh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt 1 Samuel 25:42-43\x*Kamagh…®n, Devit uan amuimning ko ghua Hebron…®n nguibar ekiam…®n apera. An amuir mam, a Jesril…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amizim, an ziam Ahinoam. An amuir igharazim, a Karmel…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amizim, an ziam Abigel. A fom…®ra Nabal…®n amuim, Nabal aremez…®ma Devit a inigha an iti.
\v 3 Devit uan gumaziba ko, an gumazibar adarasi, me bar ghua Hebron ko Hebron…®n borogh…®n itir nguibar ekiabagh apia.
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt 1 Samuel 31:11-13\x*Ez…® Judan adarazir gumaziba iza Hebron…®n otivigha, uari bagh atrivim…®n ikiasa Devit am…®sevegha, oliv…®n borem an dapanim ginge.
\p Devit atrivim…®n otogha g…®vagha kamagh…®n oraki, Jabes…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itir gumazamizir maba Sol…®n kuam afa. Jabes, a Gileat…®n nguazim…®n aven itir nguibam.
\p 
\v 5 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a gumazir maba amangiz…®, me ghua Jabesia m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa apangkuvim ikia arazir aghuim…®n Sol gamigha an kuam afa, a ian atrivim. Kamagh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian apangkuvigh deraghv…®ra ia damu.
\v 6 Ikiav…®ra Itir God dat…®r…®gh…®n guiz…®n apangkuvir arazim…®n ian akakagh…®va, zurara deraghv…®ra ia damu. Eght…® k…® uaghan ian arazir aghuir ia Sol gamizim ikarvagh deraghv…®ra ia damuam.
\v 7 Guizbang…®ra, ian Atrivim Sol areme, ez…® Judan adarazi uari bagh atrivim…®n ikiasa na m…®sefe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia tuivigh gavgavigh bizitam…®n atiatingan mark…®.‚Äù
\s1 Israelia uari bagh atrivim…®n ikiasa Isboset am…®sefe
\p 
\v 8 Filistiaba Sol m…®soghez…® an aremezir dughiam…®n, Ner…®n otarim Apner, ghua Sol…®n otarim Isboset\f + \fr 2:8 \ft Gumazir kam…®n ziam Isboset, a guizbang…®ra, Isbal o Esbal. (N…® 1 Eghaghaniba 8:33…®n gan.) Ez…® Hibrun akam ziam Isbal an akar kam…®n m…®rara ghu, ‚ÄúBal…®n gumazim.‚Äù Bal an asem…®n ziam, egha gumaziba ua ziar kam Bal osiran aghua, egha me a giragha kamagh…®n osiri, ‚ÄúBoset,‚Äù an akar kam…®n m…®rara ghu, ‚Äúaghums…®zir bizim.‚Äù\f* inigha ghua, Jordan…®n Fanem abigha ghua Mahanaim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n oto. Apner Sol…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar faragha zuir gumazir dapanim.
\v 9 Me Mahanaim…®n ikiava, Apner Isboset gamiz…®, a nguazir kabar atrivim…®n oto: Gileat, Aser, Jesril, Efraim ko Benjamin, egh a uaghan Israelian nguibaba, bar dar atrivim…®n oto.
\v 10 Sol…®n otarim Isboset 40plan azeniba itima, me Israelian atrivim…®n ikiasa anem…®sefe. Ez…® an azenir pumuningra atrivir ingangarim gami. Ez…® Judaba me Devit…®n g…®n zui,
\v 11 ez…® a Hebron…®n ikia azenir 7pla ko akuam…®n, men atrivir ingangarim gami.
\s1 Israelia Judan adarazi ko m…®sosi
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Ner…®n otarim Apner ko Sol…®n otarim Isboset, uan ingangarir gumaziba ko, me bar mogh…®ra Mahanaim…®n nguibar ekiam ategha ghua, Gibeon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n oto.
\v 13 Ez…® Seruian otarim Joap, ko Devit…®n ingangarir gumaziba, me bar mogh…®ra iza Gibeon…®n d…®par akarem…®n borogh…®n me bato. Isboset…®n adarazi d…®par akarem…®n vong…®n apiaghav itima, Devit…®n adarazi vong…®n apiaghav ti.
\v 14 Ez…® Apner kamagh…®n Joap…®n azara, ‚ÄúE m…®dorozir gumazir igiar aghui taba inight…®, me en damazibar ikararang uariv sogham.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Joap ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, me mamagh…®ra damuam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® Benjamin…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazir 12pla, me Isboset…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba, me iza Devit…®n 12plan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko uariv sosi. Ez…® Devit…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba vaghvagha, Isboset…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba vaghvagha me ko me uariv sosi.
\v 16 Me vaghvagha m…®dorozim…®n uari ab…®nasava amua, egha me vaghvagha uan apanibar dapanibar suigha, m…®dorozir sababar uan apanibar navibagh inifi. Egha 24plan gumazir kaba bar mogh…®ra iregha ariaghire. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamiziba danganir kam d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúM…®dorozir Sababar Danganim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, m…®dorozir bar ekiam ik…®zir kamning…®n tong…®n oto. Ez…® Devit…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba me Apner ko, Israelian adarazi m…®dorozim…®n me gafiragha me ab…®ni.
\v 18 Seruian otarir 3plan ziabar kara: Joap, Abisai ko Asahel, me uaghan m…®dorozir kam…®n iti. Asahel, an as…®zir atiabar m…®n bar pamtem…®n ivemari.
\v 19 Ez…® Israelia tintinibar arima, Asahel d…®kavigha Apner bagha ivegha biaghat…®gha ghua an ag…®ra.
\v 20 Ez…® Apner ik…®gha g…®rak…®rang…®n garima, Asahel an ag…®nt…®zima, Apner kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄúAsahel kar n…®rara?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Asahel ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, k…®rara.‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Egha Apner ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® nan ag…®nt…®ghan mark…®. N…® agharir guvim o k…®riam…®n mang…®. Egh n…® m…®dorozir gumazir igiar igharazitam…®n ag…®ragh an suiragh, egh an biziba inigh.‚Äù Ez…® puvat…®. Asahel tong Apner…®n akam barazi puvat…®gha, an ag…®nt…®ghav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Apner uam a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® na atakigh. K…® n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeghasa, n…® ti ifonge? K…® n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeght…®, k…® n…®n avebam Joap…®n damazim…®n bar aghumsigham.‚Äù
\v 23 Ez…® puvat…®, Asahel tong a barazir puvat…®. Kamagh amiz…®, Apner g…®rak…®rang…®n mogh…®n afuzir konim…®n Asahel…®n navim b…®raz…®ma, afuzim anem…®k…®ragha vong…®n an ak…®rir agharim…®n oto. Ez…® Asahel ir…®ghava areme. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir igharaziba iza garima, Asahel…®n kuam ir…®ghav iti, ez…® me danganir kam…®n tuivighav ikia pura gari.
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® Joap ko Abisai, aning Apner…®n ag…®ragha ghua, aruem uaghirima aning Gian nguibam…®n borogh…®n Aman m…®ghs…®am…®n oto, kar Gibeon…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim zuir tuavim.
\v 25 Aning garima, Benjamin…®n gumaziba Apner ko m…®ghs…®ar dozir mam…®n uari akuvagha, pura m…®dorozim bagha uari ar…®gha iti.
\v 26 Ez…® Apner aning…®n apigha, Joap…®n diagha ghaze, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n ami? M…®dorozir kam g…®vaghan kogham? N…® ti kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, arazir kam os…®mt…®zir bar ekiam e dan…®ngam? E ik…®zir vam…®ra. N…® dazogh…®n uan gumazibav kemeght…®, me uam en ag…®nt…®ghan kogham?‚Äù
\p 
\v 27 Joap kamagh…®n oregha a ikara, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n k…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, n…® ti akar kam…®n na m…®kemezir puvat…®z…®, nan gumaziba ian ag…®nt…®gha ghua gurum m…®zaraghan otoghan koghai.‚Äù
\v 28 Joap akar kam m…®kemegha g…®vagha, s…®gham givia Israelian ag…®nt…®ghan uan m…®dorozir gumazibar anogoroke. Ez…® me ua Israelian ag…®nt…®gh…®zir puvat…®gha m…®dorozim ag…®fa.
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® Apner uan adarazi ko me danganir kam ategha Jordan…®n danganir zarim…®n uaghiri. Egha me d…®magarim…®n danganir zarir kam…®n ghua Jordan…®n Fanem abigha vong…®n ghua, am…®mzaraghan aruer ar…®zim…®n Mahanaim…®n oto.
\p 
\v 30 Apner uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghuegha g…®vaz…®ma, Joap uan m…®dorozir gumaziba akuvagha me medi. A me mengegha kamagh…®n fo, 19plan m…®dorozir gumaziba ariaghire. Ez…® Asahel uaghan areme.
\v 31 Dughiar kam…®n, Devit…®n adarazi Benjamin…®n 360plan gumazibav soghez…® me ariaghire, kar Apner…®n adarasi.
\v 32 Ez…® Joap uan gumaziba ko, me Asahel…®n kuam inigha ghua Betlehem…®n nguibam…®n, an afeziam afazir danganim…®n anefa. Me anefagha d…®magarim…®n uamategha ghua Hebron…®n otivima, am…®nim bar tira.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n g…®n, m…®dorozim dughiar bar ruarim…®n Devit ko Sol…®n adarazir tong…®n iti. Devit…®n adarazi bar gavgavigha ghuavanaga Sol…®n adarazigh amima, me bar am…®ragha uaghiri.
\s1 Devit 6plan otariba iti
\p 
\v 2 Devit Hebron aperagha 6plan otarir kaba ini. Men ziabar kara: Amnon, an otarir ivariam, an amebam Ahinoam, a Jesril…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amizim.
\v 3 Amnon…®n g…®rara irim, Kileap, an amebam Abigel, a Karmelian amizim. Abigel faragha Nabal…®n ike, ez…® Nabal aremez…®, Devit a inigha an iti. Ez…® otarir m…®kezim, Apsalom, an amebam Maka, Maka kantri Gesur…®n Atrivim Talmain guivim.
\v 4 Namba 4…®n otarim, Adoniya, an amebam Hagit. Otarir namba 5…®n ziam, Sefatia, an amebam Abital.
\v 5 Ez…® otarir namba 6, Itream, an amebam Ekla, a Devit…®n amuim. Devit Hebron…®n ikiava otarir kaba ini.
\s1 Apner Devit ko m…®gei
\p 
\v 6 Sol…®n adarazi ko Devit…®n adarazir m…®dorozir gumaziba uariv sogha ghuav…®ra itima, Apner a Sol…®n adarazir gumazir ekiam…®n otivasava ami.
\v 7 Ez…® dughiar mam…®n, Isboset kamagh…®n akar mam Apner gasa ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® nan afeziam Sol…®n amuir dozim koma akui. Amizir kam…®n ziam Rispa, a Aian guivim. N…® tizim bagha kamagh…®n ami?‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Apner akar kam baregha atara bar osemegha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ghaze, k…® ti n…®n afiar gumazim? Egha n…® ghaze, k…® ti Judabar akurvasi? Puvat…®. N…® n…®ghn…®gh. Dughiar n…®n afeziam Sol atrivim…®n ikia iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, k…® a ko an aveghbuaba ko an namakabar g…®n zui. Egha k…® uaghan n…® ataghiz…®, Devit n…® inigha n…® gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Ez…® n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n amizir kam bagha akam na gasi, kar pura bizir k…®nim.
\v 9-10 \x - \xo 3:9-10 \xt 1 Samuel 15:28\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Devit bagha Akar Gavgavir mam ak…®righa ghaze, Devit Sol…®n adarazi batueght…®ma, me Israelian atrivibar ikian kogham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, a uab…® Devit damight…® a Israelia ko Judabar atrivim…®n ik…®va, kantrin kam bar a gativagham. Eght…® Devit kantrin kam…®n atrivim…®n ik…®, egh Dan…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n ikegh mang…® nguibar ekiam Berseban tugham. God Devit bagha d…®k…®r…®zir Akar Gavgavir kam bagh, k…® Devit…®n akuraghan koght…®, God na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham.‚Äù
\v 11 Kamagh…®n, Isboset oregha bar Apner…®n atiatigha, ua m…®geir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Apner zuam…®ra Devit bagha akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúTinara kantrin kam gativagham? K…® kamaghsua, n…® na ko akar gavgavim ak…®right…®, k…® n…®n akuragh, Israelia damight…® me bar n…®n gumazamizibara ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n Apner bagha akam amada, ‚ÄúN…®n akaba bar dera. K…® kamaghsua, n…® faragh bizir kam na koma anek…®righ. Bizir kam kamak…®n, n…® Sol…®n guivim Mikal, na bagh a inigh iz…®. Puvat…®ght…®, k…® ua n…®n ganan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt 1 Samuel 18:27\x*Egha Devit g…®n Isboset bagha akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® kamagh…®n ifonge, n…® nan amuim Mikal na bagh anemadaght…® a uamategh iz…®. A guizbang…®ra nan amuim. K…® fom…®ra 100plan Filistiabar m…®karzir mogomebar inibar a givese.‚Äù
\v 15 Ez…® Isboset kamagh…®n oregha gumazir maba amangiz…®ma, me ghua Lais…®n otarim Paltiel, a Mikal…®n pam, me ada Mikal inigha Devit bagha ize.\f + \fr 3:15 \ft N…® 1 Samuel 18:17-27 ko 25:44…®n gan.\f*
\p 
\v 16 Me Mikal inigha Devit bagha zuir dughiam…®n, Paltiel aziava Mikal…®n g…®n zui. Me ghua Bahurim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otogha, Apner kamagh…®n Paltiel m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uamategh uan d…®penim…®n mang…®.‚Äù Ez…® Paltiel an akam baregha uamatenge.
\p 
\v 17 Me t…®ghar Devit bagh mangamin dughiam…®n, Apner Israelian gumazir dapaniba bagha ghugha me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa oragh. Faragha zuir dughiar av…®ribar ia bar ifongegha ghaze, Devit en atrivim…®n ikiam.
\v 18 Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®kavigh mang…® a damight…®, an atrivim…®n otivam. Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God amizir akar kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh. A kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄòNan ingangarir gumazim Devit, k…® ingangarim a danight…®ma, a Filistiaba ko apanir igharazibar dafarim…®n, nan gumazamiziba Israelia, a ua me iniam.‚Äô ‚Äù
\v 19 Egha Apner uaghan uab…® ghua Benjamin…®n adaraziv keme. Egha g…®n uamategha Hebron…®n ghugha, Benjaminia ko Israelia damuasa ifongezir bizibar gun Devit m…®gei.
\p 
\v 20 Apner uan gumazir 20pla ko me ghua Hebron…®n Devit batozir dughiam…®n, Devit me bagha isar ekiam gami.
\v 21 Ez…® Apner g…®n kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® na ateght…®, k…® mang…®va Israelia bar me inigh iz…®t…®, me n…®n apengan ik…®s…® n…® ko akar gavgavim ak…®ram. Eght…® n…® ifongez…® mogh…®n, n…® kantrin kam…®n danganiba bar dar atrivim…®n ikiam.‚Äù Ez…® Devit uan adaraziv g…®a ghaze, ia arazir kuratam…®n Apner damuan mark…®. Egha a Apner amadaz…®ma, a navir am…®rizim sara uamategha ghu.
\s1 Joap Apner…®n m…®soghez…® an areme
\p 
\v 22 Apner Hebron…®n itir dughiam…®n, Joap ko Devit…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba itir puvat…®. Me ghua apanibav sosi. Ez…® Devit Apner amadaz…® a ghuz…®ma, an g…®rara Joap…®n adarazi me uan apanibav suegha, me da inizir biziba inigha uam Hebron…®n otifi.
\v 23 Ez…® Joap ko an g…®n zuir m…®dorozir gumaziba bar Hebron otivigha, Joap kamagh…®n oraki, Apner iza Atrivim Devit…®n gani, ez…® Devit Apner…®n m…®soghan gumazibar anogoregha anemadaz…®ma, a navir am…®rizim sara ghu.
\p 
\v 24 Kamagh amiz…®, Joap ghua atrivim…®n gara an m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúMe ghaze, Apner iza n…® batoz…®ma n…® anetaghiz…®ma, a uamategha navir am…®rizim sara ghu.
\v 25 N…® ti Ner…®n otarim Apner…®n arazibagh fozir puvat…®? A n…® gifara n…®n ganasa izi. A n…®n akurvaghasa izir puvat…®. A n…®n danganir n…® aruiba ko, n…® amir biziba, a modogh bar dar gan da asavsuighasa ize, egh a uamategh iz…® n…® ko m…®sogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 26 Joap m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gamigha uamategha ghu. A ua Apner inigh izasa gumaziba amadaz…®, me an g…®nt…®gha an g…®n ghue. Gumazir kaba ghua Siran mozirpam…®n a batogha, uam a inigha izi. Dughiar kam…®n, Devit bizir Joap amir kam g…®fozir puvat…®.
\v 27 Apner iza Hebron…®n otozir dughiam…®n, Joap a inigha ghua nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akam…®n, a ko tugha n…®m…®ra a ko m…®k…®masa. Egha aning tughav itir dughiar kam…®n, Joap uan afuam inigha Apner…®n navim b…®raz…®ma an areme. Joap uan dozim Asahel…®n ovevem ikarvagha, Apner b…®raz…® an areme.
\p 
\v 28 Me g…®n bizir kam…®n gun Devit…®n m…®kemez…®, a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God fo, k…® Apner…®n suiragha a m…®soghez…® an aremezir puvat…®. Nan gumazamiziba uaghan os…®mt…®zitam an itir puvat…®. Joap uab…®ra, kar an os…®mt…®zim.
\v 29 Kamagh amiz…®, an ghuzim Joap…®n dapanim gir…®va, an afeziam…®n d…®penim…®n itir darazi sara bar me giram. K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, Joap…®n d…®penim…®n aven itir gumaziba zurazurara, men tarazi g…®n lepan ar…®mariam ik…®t…®, men tarazi duar kurar m…®dir puvat…®ziba ik…®t…®, men tarazi amizibar ingangaribar amuam, eght…® men tarazi apaniba m…®dorozibar me m…®soght…®ma me ar…®ghir…®t…®, men tarazi zurazurara daghebar otevegham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 30 Arazir kam…®n, Apner faragha Gibeon…®n m…®dorozim…®n aven Joap ko Abisain dozim, Asahel m…®soghez…® an areme. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Joap ko Abisai aning uan dozim…®n ovevem ikarvagha, Apner…®n m…®soghez…® an areme.
\s1 Me Apner…®n kuam afa
\p 
\v 31-32 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n Joap uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uan korotiaba abigh…®va, azirakar korotiabar aghuigh, egh ia Apner bagh azi.‚Äù Me Hebron…®n anefa. Dughiar me Apner…®n kuam inigha gumazir kuaba afir danganim…®n zuima, Devit Apner…®n akuriam…®n g…®rara zui. Devit gumazamiziba ko me mozim…®n borogh…®n tuivighav ikia, bar mogh…®ra puv…®ram azi.
\v 33 Egha Devit Apner bagha azirakar igiar kam bange:
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúApner gumazir onganim puvat…®.
\q2 A tizim bagha pura kamagh…®n areme?
\q1 
\v 34 Me an suemning ko dafarimning ikezir puvat…®,
\q2 me a gifaragha a m…®soghez…® an areme,
\q1 me gumazir kurabagh ami mogh…®n,
\q2 me a gami.‚Äù
\b
\m Devit ighiar kam gamigha g…®vaz…®, gumazamiziba uam Apner bagha azi.
\p 
\v 35 Bizir kabar g…®n, gumazamiziba Devit m…®g…®a ghaze, aruem ikiav…®ra iti, n…® daghetam am…®. Ez…® an aghuagha akar gavgavir mam…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® daghetam ameghan kogh ik…® mang…® guarat…®zim…®n tugham. Aruem t…®ghar mag…®r…®t…® k…® daghetam ameght…®, God na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham.‚Äù
\v 36 Ez…® gumazamiziba atrivim…®n akar kam baregha, men naviba am…®raz…® me bar akonge. Guizbang…®ra, me atrivim amir biziba bar dar ganigha da bagha bar akonge.
\v 37 Devit…®n adarazi ko Israelian gumazamiziba bar, Devit aruer kam…®n amizir bizibagh fo, Atrivim Devit, Apner…®n m…®soghez…® aremezir gumazim, an a ko navir vam…®ra itir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 38 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n uan ingangarir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa oragh. Dat…®r…®gh…®n, e Israelia en faragha zuir gumazir gavgavir mam aremegha g…®fa.
\v 39 Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God na m…®sevez…®, k…® atrivim…®n oto. Ez…® k…® uab…® gavgaviba puvat…®. K…® Seruian otarimning…®n arazir kuram ikarvaghan ibura. Aning bar gavgafi. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® aning amizir arazir kurar kam ikarvaghs…®, ivezir kuram aning dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\c 4
\s1 Gumazir pumuning Isboset m…®soghez…® an areme
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Sol…®n otarim Isboset kamagh…®n oraki, me Hebron…®n nguibar ekiam…®n Apner m…®soghez…® an areme, ez…® a d…®gavir kuram gamigha bar oseme. Ez…® Israelia bar atiatingi.
\v 2 Ez…® Isboset…®n m…®dorozir gumazir pumuning, aning m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim…®n ikia ghua apaniba ko m…®sosi. Aning…®n ziamning, Bana ko Rekap, aning Rimon…®n otarimning. Rimon, a Berot…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazir mam. Gumazamiziba Benjamin…®n adarazi bagha Berot…®n nguibar ekiam ginaba, kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir kamning aning Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazir aven iti.
\v 3 Guiz…®n Berot…®n gumazamiziba, me faragha aregha, dat…®r…®gh…®n pura nguibar igharazibar gumazibar m…®n Gitaim…®n nguibam…®n iti.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt 2 Samuel 9:3\x*Sol…®n otarim Jonatan, an otarir vam…®ra iti, an ziam Mefiboset.\f + \fr 4:4 \ft Gumazir kam…®n ziam, a Meribal. (N…® 1 Eghaghaniba 8:34…®n gan.) Ziar kam…®n akuar abuananam, a, ‚ÄúBal,‚Äù an asem…®n ziam. Ez…® g…®n me ua ziar kam Bal osiran aghua, egha a giragha kamagh…®n osiri, ‚ÄúBoset.‚Äù An akar kam…®n m…®rara ghu, ‚ÄúAghums…®zir Bizim.‚Äù Ez…® gumazir kam…®n ziam kamagh…®n oto, ‚ÄúMeriboset,‚Äù o ‚ÄúMefiboset.‚Äù\f* Mefiboset 5plan azeniba itima, Sol ko Jonatan areme. Dughiar kam…®n, Jesril…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumaziba, me Jonatan…®n adarazi bagha akam amaga ghaze, Jonatan…®n apaniba a m…®soghez…®ma an areme. Ez…® an adarazi akar kam baraki, ez…® amizir Mefiboset…®n garim a inigha arav ghu. Amizim pamtem…®n ivemarima, Mefiboset degiaghir…®, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n an dagarimning an ikufi.
\p 
\v 5 Dughiar mam…®n, aveghbuamning Rekap ko Bana, aning Isboset bagha ghua, aruer ar…®zim…®n an d…®penim…®n oto. Dughiar kam…®n, Isboset avughsava uan akuir m…®siam…®n ir…®ghav iti.
\v 6-7 Aning Isboset m…®soghasa witba iniamin abazim gamua a gat…®n, an akuir danganim…®n aven ghua garima, a uan m…®siam…®n akui. Aning m…®dorozir sabam…®n an navim b…®raz…®ma an areme. Ez…® aning an f…®rim atugha garima, gumaziba puvat…®z…®, aning an dapanim inigha ghu. Aning d…®magarim…®n Jordan…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim…®n ghua,
\v 8 am…®mzaraghan Hebron…®n nguibar ekiam…®n oto. Egha Isboset…®n dapanim inigha ghua Devit…®n akagha, kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim, n…® kagh gan. N…®n apanim Sol, an otarim Isboset…®n dapanim kara. Sol fom…®ra n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeghasa tuaviba buri, kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…®n akurvagha Sol uan boriba ko men arazir kuraba ikarvasi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n aning…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God zurara ikia, an arazir kurar kamagh…®n garibar aven ua na ini. Ez…® an ziam…®n k…® kamagh…®n guizbang…®ra gua m…®k…®mam.
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt 2 Samuel 1:1-16\x*Dughiar k…® Siklak…®n nguibam…®n itim…®n, gumazir mam iza na batogha ghaze, Sol aremegha g…®fa. A ghaze, k…® ti an akam gakuegham. Ez…® puvat…®. K…® m…®dorozir gumazibav kemez…® me an suiragha, a m…®soghez…®ma an areme. Kar mati, akar kurar a na bagha inigha izezim…®n ivezir kuram k…® a gan…®ngi.
\v 11 Ez…® gua dat…®r…®gh…®n pura gumazir k…®nir uan d…®penim gakuim m…®soghez…®ma an areme. Gua gumazir bar kuramning. Gua ghaze, k…® ti gua ateght…®ma gua ikiam? Bar puvat…®. K…® gua amizir arazir kurar kam ikarvaghs…® gua gas…®ghasight…®, gua ua nguazir kam…®n ikian kogham.‚Äù
\v 12 Egha Devit akar gavgavim uan m…®dorozir gumazibagh an…®ga ghaze, me Rekap ko Bana aning m…®sueght…® aning aremegh. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba aning m…®suegha, aning…®n sueroghofariba aghoregha da inigha ghua Hebron…®n d…®par akarer mam…®n borogh…®n da agui. Egha Isboset…®n dapanim, m…®dorozir gumaziba a inigha ghua Hebron…®n kuaba afir danganim…®n, Apner…®n mozir kamra anefa.
\c 5
\s1 Devit Israelia ko Judabar atrivim…®n oto
\r (1 Eghaghaniba 11:1-9; 14:1-7)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® bizir kam…®n g…®n, Israelian anababa vaghvagha dar gumazir dapaniba bar iza Hebron…®n nguibam…®n Devit…®n gara, kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh. E bar inivaf…®zir vam…®ra ko ghuzir vam…®ra.
\v 2 Sol fom…®ra en atrivim…®n itima, n…® m…®dorozibar Israelia e bagha en m…®dorozir gumazibar faragha zui. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…® m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazim…®n m…®n ik…®, en gumazamizibagh ativagham. Egh en atrivim…®n otogham.‚Äù
\v 3 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelian gumazir dapaniba iza, Hebron…®n nguibam…®n otogha, Atrivim Devit…®n bighan uari akuvaz…®, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavir mam me ko a gami. Ez…® me borem isa an dapanim ginga, magh…®ram anem…®sevez…® a Israelian atrivim…®n oto.
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4-5 \xt 1 Atriviba 2:11; 1 Eghaghaniba 3:4; 29:27\x*Devit 30plan azeniba ikia atrivim…®n oto. Egha 40plan azenibar atrivim…®n iti.
\v 5 Devit 7plan azeniba ko 6plan iak…®nibar, Hebron…®n Judabar atrivim…®n ike. Egha 33plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n Israelia ko Judaba, uaghara me gativagha men gari.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 5:6 \xt Josua 15:63; Gumazir Dapaniba 1:21\x*Dughiar mam…®n, Atrivim Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua Jerusalem iniasa m…®sosi. Jerusalem a Jebusian nguibamra. Jebusia ghaze, Devit men nguibam inian kogham, egha me d…®bovir akabar a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa bar en nguibar ekiam…®n aven izan kogham. Gumazir damazir okav…®r…®ziba ko suer am…®raziba, me pura iz…® ia izamin tuavim ap…®righam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® puvat…®, men akaba pura magh ire, Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua me m…®sogha men nguibar ekiar d…®vazir gavgavim itim ini. Nguibar ekiar kam…®n ziam Saion. Ez…® g…®n gumazamiziba a d…®bora ghaze, Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam.
\v 8 Dughiar Devit nguibar ekiar kam inizim…®n, a kamagh…®n uan m…®dorozir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE nguibar ekiar kam inis…®va, tuavir d…®r…®zir Jebusia d…®pam iniasa aruim…®n aven mang…®va nguibar ekiam…®n otogham. Egh e damazir okav…®r…®ziba ko suer kuraba ko m…®sogham. Gumazir kamagh gariba, me nan apanibar m…®n iti.‚Äù
\p Gumazamiziba dat…®r…®gh…®n Devit…®n akam g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra ikia kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúDamazir okav…®r…®ziba ko suer am…®raziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven mangan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Devit g…®n ghua Saion…®n nguibar ekiar gavgavir kam gapera. Egha a ziam a gat…®gha ghaze, Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam. Egha Devit m…®kemez…®ma, ingangarir gumaziba nguibar ekiam…®n d…®penir av…®ribar ingariz…® da nguibar ekiam azui. Me danganir konir nguaziba akunizim…®n, d…®peniba faraghav…®ra azenan dar ingara, egha nguibar ekiam…®n aven izi.
\v 10 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim Devit ko itima, bizir kam bang…®n, Devit atrivir gavgavim…®n ikia ghua bar ekevegha ikia mamagh…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 11 Tair…®n nguibar ekiam…®n Atrivim Hiram, a uan gavman…®n ingangarir gumazir dapaniba Devit bagha me amada. A uaghan Atrivim Devit…®n d…®penim…®n ingarasa, temer sidaba ko, d…®penibar ingarir gumaziba ko gumazir dag…®abar ingariba, a me amangi. Ez…® me Devit bagha atrivir d…®penim…®n ingari.
\v 12 Devit bizir kabar gari, da a bagha izima a kamagh…®n fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God guizbang…®ra Israelian atrivim…®n ikiasa a ginaba. A uaghan kamagh…®n fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan gumazamiziba bar men akurvaghasa, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a kantri Israel gamima, a bar dera.
\p 
\v 13 Devit Hebron ategha iza Jerusalem gaperazir dughiam…®n, an amuir igharazir maba uam ada inigha dar iti, a uaghan amuir dozir maba uaghan dar iti. Ez…® an amuir kaba, Jerusalem…®n otariba ko guivir maba bate.
\v 14 An otaribar ziabar kara: Samua, Sobap, Natan, Solomon,
\v 15 Iphar, Elisua, Nefek, Jafia,
\v 16 Elisama, Eliada ko Elifelet.
\s1 Devit Filistiabav sogha me ab…®ni
\r (1 Eghaghaniba 14:8-17)
\p 
\v 17 Filistiaba kamagh…®n oraki, Israelia Devit am…®sevez…®ma a men atrivim…®n oto. Ez…® Filistiaba mang…® me m…®sogh Devit…®n suighasa zui. Me bizir kam damuasa amima Devit fogha, uan danganir mogomer gavgavim…®n uaghir…®.
\v 18 Filistiaba iza Refaim…®n danganir zarim…®n otogha tintinibar ghuegha mongegha iti.
\v 19 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azara, ‚ÄúK…® mang…®va Filistian kabav sogham o? K…® mang…® me ko m…®soght…®, n…® me is…® na dafarim dar…®gham o?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, n…® mang…®. K…® me is…® n…®n dafarim dat…®ght…®, n…® m…®dorozim…®n me ab…®ragham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® Devit ghua Filistiabav sogha me ab…®ragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God mati aperiam otogha, pamtem…®n ivemara nan damazim…®n nan apaniba ab…®agharigha me gas…®ghas…®ki.‚Äù
\p Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me danganir kam d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God Aperiam…®n M…®n Pamten Ivemara Apaniba Ab…®aghar…®si.‚Äù
\v 21 Ez…® Filistiaba uan marvir guaba ategha are. Ez…® Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko men marvir guar kaba inigha ghue.
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Filistiaba g…®n ua izegha, Refaim…®n danganir zarim…®n tintinibar uari aghamsigha iti.
\v 23 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azara, ‚ÄúK…® manmagh…®n damuam?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa me m…®soghs…® mang…®va, men guabar mogh…®n mangan mark…®. Ia modogh men g…®rak…®rang…®n mogh…®n mang…®, egh temer balsamba tuivighav iti nagh…®n, m…®soghs…®v…®ra gan ik…®.
\v 24 \x - \xo 5:24 \xt 2 Atriviba 7:6\x*Ia oraght…®ma n…®g…®nim mati, gumaziba temer kabar ghuabagh is…®n daruam. Eght…® ia fogh suam, k…® uab…® Filistiabav soghs…® ian faragh mangam. Ia n…®g…®nir kam baraghamin dughiam…®n, ia magh…®ra ivemar mang…® me m…®sogh.‚Äù
\v 25 Ez…® Devit Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®kemez…® mogh…®ram amigha, Filistiabar ag…®ragha bar me m…®suaghar…®ki. Israelia me m…®sogha Gibeon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikegha ghua Geser…®n nguibar ekiam…®n tu.
\c 6
\s1 Me Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam inigha Jerusalem…®n ize
\r (1 Eghaghaniba 13:1-14; 15:25--16:6; 16:43)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Devit deraghav…®ra m…®sozir gumazir bar aghuiba uam me akufa. Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir kaba, men d…®bobonim 30,000.
\v 2 \x - \xo 6:2 \xt Ua Me Ini 25:22\x*Devit me inigha God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam iniasa Judan nguazim…®n itir nguibam Balan zui. Me Boksiar kam m…®g…®a ghaze, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, kar an Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam. Boksiar kam, ensel…®n bar gavgavir pumuning…®n nedazimning, a gis…®n ikia mati, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n atrivir dabirabim.
\v 3 \x - \xo 6:3 \xt 1 Samuel 7:1-2\x*Ez…® Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua Balan nguibar ekiam…®n otogha, m…®ghs…®ar dozir mam a gis…®n Abinadap…®n d…®penim…®n ghue. Egha me God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam inigh mangasa, karis…®n igiar mam inigha Boksiar kam isa a gis…®n anet…®. Ez…® Abinadap…®n otarimning, Usa ko Ahio, aning karis…®n igiar kam…®n akua tuavim…®n zui.
\v 4 Ez…® Ahio karis…®n faragha zui.
\v 5 Ez…® Devit Israelia ko me bar mogh…®ra ghuava, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n bar akongegha pamtem ighiabagh amua, ararer aghuim gamua an ziam fe. Me gitaba ko buaba, tambarinba ko d…®b…®arir ararer guar av…®riba inigha dav sosi.
\p 
\v 6 Me ghua gumazir mam…®n nguazir as…®zim…®n oto, gumazir kam…®n ziam Nakon. Kar me wit…®n ov…®zibar iniba kua dar dagheba isir danganim. Danganir kam…®n bulmakauba daghdazima, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam irasava ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Usa uan agharim amadagha Boksiam…®n suira.
\v 7 Usa ghaze, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam ti pura bizim, egha an suira. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar puv…®ra Usan an…®ngaghegha atara a m…®soghez…®, an Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n m…®riam nagh…®ram areme.
\v 8 Devit garima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan an…®ngagharim Usa gingez…® an areme. Ez…® Devit bar God baseme. Egha me danganir kam d…®bora ghaze, God uan an…®ngagharim Usa ginge, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n me uaghan kamagh…®ra a d…®borav…®ra iti.\f + \fr 6:8 \ft Akar kam ‚Äúdat…®r…®gh…®n,‚Äù an en dughiar kam m…®geir puvat…®. A dughiar gumazim ak…®nafarir kam osirizim m…®gei.\f*
\p 
\v 9 Devit dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n atiatigha ghaze, ‚ÄúManmaghsu, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam iz…® na ko ikiam?‚Äù
\v 10 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Devit Boksiam inigh Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n mangan aghuagha, a inigha Jerusalem…®n zuir tuavim ategha ghua, Get…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazir mam, Obetidom…®n d…®penim…®n anet…®.
\v 11 \x - \xo 6:11 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 26:4-5\x*Ez…® Boksiam 3plan iak…®nibar Obetidom…®n d…®penim…®n iti. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar deraghav…®ra Obetidom ko an adarazi gami.
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Atrivim Devit g…®n kamagh…®n oraki, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam Obetidom ko itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Obetidom ko an adarazi ko an biziba bar, deraghav…®ra me gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Devit uamategha Obetidom…®n d…®penim…®n ghugha, God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam inigh ua Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n izasava ami. Bizir kam bagha gumazamiziba bar akonge.
\v 13 Gumaziba d…®kavigha Boksiam inigha uan sueba 6plan dughiabar da akura ghua tuifi, ez…® Devit Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofa gami. A bulmakaun apurir mam ko bulmakaun igiar m…®karzim sara itir mam inigha ofa gami.
\v 14 Egha Devit ofa gamir gumazim…®n korotiar otevir azenan azuir dirir mam arugha, an sazimning uab…® gike. Egha ziar ekiam Ikiav…®ra Itir God gan…®ga, an damazim…®n ighiabagh amua pamtem uab…® fa uab…® akuri.
\v 15 Me Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam atera Jerusalem…®n zuima, Devit Israelia ko me bar mogh…®ra arazir kamram amua, bar akongegha pamtem…®n diava s…®ghabagh ivi.
\p 
\v 16 Me Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam atera Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n aven izir dughiam…®n, Sol…®n guivim Mikal winduan tughav ikia men gari. A uan pam Atrivim Devit…®n garima, a ighiabagh amuava Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n tintinibar uab…® fakurava, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fe. Devit amir arazir kam, Mikal bar a gifongezir puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…® a navir kuram Devit…®n ikia a baseme.
\v 17 Ez…® me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam isava, Devit a bagha ingarizir purirpenim…®n aven anet…®. Egha Devit ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba ko, gumazamiziba God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofabagh ami.
\v 18 Devit ofabagh amigha g…®vagha, kamagh…®n gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, a uan ziam…®n deraghv…®ra ia damu.‚Äù
\v 19 \x - \xo 6:19-20 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 16:43\x*Egha Devit dagheba isa bar gumazamizibagh an…®ngi. Gumaziba ko amiziba vaghvagha bret ko as…®zir tuzir me avim…®n tueziba ko wain…®n ov…®zir me apuziziba, me bar ada ini. Me da inigha g…®vagha, me uamategha uan nguibabar ghue.
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® Devit uamategha uan d…®penim…®n ghugha, uan ik…®zim deragh me damuasa, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azangasava ami. Ez…® Sol…®n guivim Mikal d…®penim ategha azenan iza Devit m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAme, Israelian atrivim uan ziar ekiam akakagha, bibiamra bar deraghav…®ra uab…® fakuri. Ez…® an ingangarir gumazir dapanibar, ingangarir amizir k…®niba bar an gani. N…®n arazir kam, mati gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®zim amir arazim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ziar ekiam isa Ikiav…®ra Itir Godra dan…®ngasa an damazim…®n ighiam banga uab…® fa uab…® akuri. A uab…® n…®n afeziam…®n ik…®zim…®n danganim inigh na dan…®ngasa na ginabaz…®, k…® an gumazamizibar dapanim…®n ikiam, kar Israelia. Ez…® k…® an ziam fasa ighiabagh amuav…®ra iti.
\v 22 K…® uan ziam bar aneb…®ragh, egh an damazim…®n pura bizir k…®nim…®n m…®n ikiam. Eght…® ingangarir amizir n…® m…®geir kaba, me ziar ekiam na dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\v 23 Ez…® bizir kam bang…®n, Sol…®n guivim Mikal, a borir tam batezir puvat…®gha ikia ghuava areme.
\c 7
\s1 Akam inigha izir gumazim Natan, God…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim Devit gan…®ngi
\r (1 Eghaghaniba 17:1-15)
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar maba g…®vaz…®ma, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Atrivim Devit gamiz…®, apanir an okariziba ua izava a ko m…®sozir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uan d…®penim…®n bar derav…®ram aperaghav ikia avughsi.
\v 2 Egha atrivim kamagh…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Natan m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® d…®penir aghuir me sidan temebar ingarizim gaperaghav iti. Ez…® God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam, a purirpenim…®n iti. Bizir kam ti derazir puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® Natan atrivim ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God n…® ko iti. Kamagh…®n bizir tizim n…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n izi, n…® a damus…® puram a damu.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® d…®magarir kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Natan m…®g…®a ghaze,
\v 5 ‚ÄúN…® mang…® nan ingangarir gumazim Devit m…®k…®m suam: Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, n…® nan D…®penir k…® aven ikiamim…®n ingaramin gumazir k…® m…®sevezim puvat…®.
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúK…® d…®penir ekiabar aven itir puvat…®. Dughiar k…® Isip…®n ua Israelia inizim…®n, k…® tintinibar zuir dughiaba, k…® Purirpenim…®n averara iti.
\v 7 K…® danganir av…®ribar Israelia, ia koma aruava, kamagh…®n ian gumazir dapanir k…® m…®sevezir tam…®n azarazir puvat…®, ‚ÄòN…® tizim bagha na bagha temer sidan d…®penir tam…®n ingarizir puvat…®?‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua Natan m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n nan ingangarir gumazim Devit m…®k…®m: K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, n…® sipsipbagh eghuva dar garir dughiam…®n, n…® nan gumazamiziba Israelia, men gumazir dapanim…®n ikiasa k…® n…® am…®sefe.
\v 9 N…® zuir danganiba bar, k…® n…® ko iti. Egha k…® n…®n apaniba ab…®raz…®ma, n…® me gas…®ghas…®ki. Nguazir kam…®n gumazibar ziaba ekevez…® mogh…®n, k…® n…®n ziam damight…® a bar ekevegham.
\v 10-11 K…® uan gumazamiziba Israelia bagha nguazir mam am…®sefe. K…® an me aright…®, me uan nguibam…®n m…®n deraghv…®ra a dapiagh ik…®va uam atiatingan kogham. Eght…® gumazir kuraba fom…®ra me gamiz…® mogh…®n, ua me damuan kogham. Ian ovaviba fom…®ra nguazir kam inizir dughiam…®n ikegha, iza k…® ia bagha m…®sevezir gumazir dapanibar dughiam…®n, ian apaniba ia gas…®ghas…®ghav…®ra iti. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® apanibar tuaviba ap…®right…®, me ua me gas…®ghas…®ghan kogham. K…® n…®n adarazi ateght…®, me ik…®va n…® bagh ovavir boriba batam.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 7:12 \xt Onger Akaba 89:3-4; 132:11; Jon 7:42; Aposel 2:30\x*‚ÄúN…® aremeght…®, me n…® afaghamin dughiam…®n, k…® n…®n boribar tong…®n otarir tam am…®seveght…®, an atrivir gavgavim…®n otoght…®, bizitam a d…®kab…®raghan kogham.
\v 13 Atrivir kamra, a na bagh D…®penim…®n ingaram. Eght…® k…® an ovavir boribar amight…®, me g…®n atrivibar ik…® gavgavigh mamagh…®ra ikiam.
\v 14 \x - \xo 7:14 \xt Onger Akaba 89:26-27; 2 Korin 6:18; Hibru 1:5\x*Eght…® k…® uab…® ia inigh, egh ian Afeziam…®n m…®n ik…®t…®, ia nan borim…®n m…®n ikiam. Egh an arazir kuram damight…® k…® m…®zazim a gasegham. Mati afeziam uan borim m…®zazim a gasi mogh…®n k…® a damuam.
\v 15 Egh k…® zurara an apangkuvam. K…® faragha Sol batoghez…® n…® an danganim iniz…® mogh…®n, k…® ak…®rim ragh an otarim gasaraghan kogham.
\v 16 \x - \xo 7:16 \xt Onger Akaba 89:36-37\x*Eght…® n…®n adarazi g…®vaghan kogham. K…® n…®n ik…®zim…®n aven gumazibar amut…®, me atrivibar otiv mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\v 17 Natan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akaba baregha g…®vagha, ghua God an akazir biziba bar dar gun Devit m…®keme.
\s1 Devit Ekiam ko m…®gei
\r (1 Eghaghaniba 17:16-27)
\p 
\v 18 Atrivim Devit, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam baregha g…®vagha, an Purirpenim…®n aven ghugha an damazim…®n kamagh…®n a ko m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan Ekiam, k…® tina, n…® arazir aghuir av…®ribar na gami. Ez…® k…® uan adarazi ko, e ziar ekiaba puvat…®. Ez…® n…® fom…®ra deraghav…®ra na gamua iza dat…®r…®gh…®n tu.
\v 19 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® ghaze, arazir aghuir n…® e gamizir kaba ti n…®n damazim…®n bizir muziariba, egha n…® arazir igharazir mam…®n ua na gami. N…® uan ingangarir gumazim…®n ovavir borir g…®n otivamibar amuamin bizim…®n gun na m…®keme. O Ikiav…®ra Itir God k…® gumazir k…®nim, ez…® n…® bar bizir ekiabar amuasa dar nan akakasi.
\v 20 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan Ekiam, k…® manmagh…®n n…® m…®k…®mam? K…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, ez…® n…® na g…®fogha g…®fa.
\v 21 N…® uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua uan ingangarir gumazim bagha bizir ekiar kam gami. Egha n…® uan akar d…®k…®r…®zir ekiaba nan akakasi.
\v 22 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en Ekiam, n…®n gavgavim bar ekevez…®, tav ua n…®n m…®n itir puvat…®. E uan inazibar akatoribar oraghiz…® mogh…®n, n…® uab…®ra bar guiz…®n God.
\v 23 \x - \xo 7:23 \xt God…®n Araziba 4:34\x*E Israelia Isip…®n kalabus…®n itima n…® uam e ini, egha n…® e gamiz…® e n…®n gumazamizibar otifi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, nguazir kam…®n gumazamizir igharaziba me, e n…®n gumazamizibar m…®n garir puvat…®. E n…®n gumazamiziba kantrin kam…®n otogha itima, n…® bizir aghuiba ko bizir ekiar av…®ribar en akura. N…® gumazamizir igharaziba batuegha men asebagh as…®ghas…®ghiz…®, e iza men nguazim ini. Kamagh…®n amiz…® kantriba bar dar gumazamiziba ziar ekiam n…® gan…®di.
\v 24 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® Israelia e gamiz…®, e zurara kamagh…®ra n…®n gumazamizibar ikiam. Eght…® n…® uab…® en God…®n ikiam.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgavim, n…® uan ingangarir gumazim, ko an adarazi bagha amizir akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam, k…® kamaghsua, n…® a damight…® a zurara kamagh…®ra ik…®.
\v 26 Eght…® gumazamiziba bizir n…® amir kabar gan…®va, ziar ekiam n…® dan…®ngam. Egh me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim a Israelian God.‚Äô Egh n…® zurara nan adarazir amut…® me atrivibar otivam.
\v 27 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, n…® Israelia en God. N…® kamagh…®n nan aka, n…® nan ovavir boribar amut…®, me zurara gavgavigh ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, k…® n…® ko m…®k…®man atiatir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 28 ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® nan Ekiam, n…® uab…® guizbang…®ra God, n…® uan akar d…®k…®r…®zibar g…®n ghua biziba bar dagh ami. Egh n…® uan ingangarir gumazim bagha akar d…®k…®r…®zir aghuir kam a damut…®, a guizbang…®ram otogh.
\v 29 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® nan Ekiam, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, k…® kamagh…®n ifonge, n…® akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, egh nan ik…®zim deraghv…®ra me damu. Eght…® ovavir borir nan g…®n izamiba, n…®n damazim…®n ik…® zurara kamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\c 8
\s1 Devit apaniba ab…®ni
\r (1 Eghaghaniba 18:1-17)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® g…®n, Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua ua Filistiaba ko m…®sosi. Egha me Filistiabav sogha me ab…®ni, kamagh…®n amiz…®, Filistiaba ua Israelia gativazir puvat…®.
\v 2 Egha g…®n, Devit ua uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua Moapia m…®sogha me ab…®ni. A men m…®dorozir gumaziba gaghora me m…®geima, me 3plan b…®zir ruaribar nguazim gireghav iti. Egha a gumazir b…®zir faragha itiba ko b…®zir namba 2…®n itibav g…®a ghaze, me aremegham. Egha namba 3…®n gumazir b…®zim m…®g…®a ghaze, me aremeghan kogham. Ez…® Moapia Devit…®n apengan ikia dag…®aba isa a gan…®di.
\v 3 Ez…® Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua kantri Soban atrivim ko m…®sosi, an ziam Hadateser, a Rehop…®n otarim. Soba, a Sirian kantrin nguibar ekiar mam. Dughiar kam…®n Hadateser uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha apanibav soghasa ghua, Yufretis…®n Fanem…®n amadaghan nguazir otevitam ua bagh a iniasa zui. Ez…® Devit…®n adarazi me batogha, m…®dorozim…®n me ab…®ni.
\v 4 Egha Devit Hadateser…®n m…®dorozir gumazir av…®riba ini. A 20,000plan m…®dorozir gumaziba isa, 1,700plan m…®dorozir gumazir hoziabagh apiaghira m…®soziba ini. Egha Devit uaghan, 100plan karisbagh etuir hoziaba ini. A uaghan hoziar igharazibar suer ag…®riba aghorez…®, da daruan ibura.
\p 
\v 5 Dughiar kam…®n Sirian Damaskus…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itiba, Me Atrivim Hadateser…®n akuragha m…®soghasa ghue. Ez…® Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, me Sirian m…®dorozir gumazir 22,000plan m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.
\v 6 Ez…® Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba Sirian kantrin tintinibar me ar…®ki. Ez…® Sirian gumazamiziba Devit…®n apengan ikiava dag…®aba isa a gan…®di. Danganir Devit m…®soghasa zuiba bar, Ikiav…®ra Itir God an akurvazima, an apaniba ab…®ri.
\v 7 Devit garima, Hadateser…®n m…®dorozir gumazir dapaniba gol…®n ingarizir oraba ateri. Ez…® David orar kaba inigha Jerusalem…®n ghu.
\v 8 A uaghan, Hadateser…®n nguibar ekiamning Beta, ko Berotai, aning…®n bras…®n av…®riba ini.
\p 
\v 9 Kantri Hamat…®n Atrivim Toi, an orazi, Devit Hadateser…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ab…®nigha g…®fa.
\v 10 Dughiar av…®ribar Hadateser faragha Toin apanim gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Devit Hadateser…®n m…®soghezir bizim bagha, Atrivim Toi bar akonge. Kamagh…®n Toi, uan otarim Joram, Devit bagha anemada. Egha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® nan dughiar aghuim a dan…®ngigh. Egh kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam, K…® orazi, n…® Hadateser ab…®ragha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® bizir n…® amizir kam bagha bar akonge.‚Äù Ez…® Joram Devit bagha ghua bizir aghuir me gol ko silva ko bras…®n ingariziba a gan…®di.
\v 11 Ez…® Devit bizir aghuir kaba inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fasa dagh inaba, eght…® da God baghv…®ra ikiam. A kantrin igharaziba bar dav sogha inizir golba ko silvaba, a kamagh…®ra dagh ami.
\v 12 Devit Idomia\f + \fr 8:12 \ft Hibrun akam ghaze ‚ÄúSiriaba.‚Äù Egha me fom…®ra akar kam Grik…®n akam…®n a giragha an osiri, ‚ÄúIdomia.‚Äù Guizbang…®ra, Hibrun akam ti faragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIdomia,‚Äù ez…® g…®n me pazav an osiri. N…® uaghan 1 Eghaghaniba 18:11…®n gan.\f* ko Moapia, Amonia, Filistia, Amalekia, ko Soban Atrivim Hadateser, a me da gol ko silvan kaba ini.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 8:13 \xt Onger Akaba 60:1\x*Devit g…®n uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko Idomia ko m…®soghasa, Danganir Zarir Amangs…®zir Av…®rim Itim…®n ghu. Egha me Idomian 18,000plan gumazibav soghez…® me ariaghire. Ez…® gumazamiziba akar kam baregha ziar ekiam Devit gan…®ngi.\f + \fr 8:13 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\v 14 Ez…® Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba kantri Idom…®n tintinibar me ar…®ki. Ez…® Idomian gumazamiziba Devit…®n apengan ikiava, dag…®aba isa a gan…®di. Danganir Devit m…®soghasa zuiba bar, Ikiav…®ra Itir God an akurvazima, an apaniba ab…®ri.
\p 
\v 15 Devit Israelia bar me gativagha, guiz…®n arazibar deraghav…®ra uan gumazamizibagh ami.
\v 16 Seruian otarim Joap, a m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim. Ez…® Ahilut…®n otarim Jehosafat, a gavman…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazir faragha zuim.
\v 17 Ez…® Sadok ko Ahimelek, aning ofa gamir gumazimning. Sadok, a Ahitup…®n otarim, ez…® Ahimelek, a Abiatar…®n otarim. Ez…® Seraia, an atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim.
\v 18 Ez…® Jehoiadan otarim Benaia, a Devit geghuvir m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapanim. Kar Keret ko Pelet…®n adarazir gumaziba. Ez…® Devit…®n otariba me ofa gamir gumazibar m…®n iti.
\c 9
\s1 Devit deragha Mefiboset gami
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 9:1 \xt 1 Samuel 20:15-17\x*Dughiar mam Devit kamagh…®n gumazibar azara, ‚ÄúSol…®n adarazir gumazitaba ikiav…®ra iti, o puvat…®? Tarazi ik…®t…®ma, k…® deragh me damuasa. K…® Jonatan na gamizir apangkuvir arazim ikarvaghasa.‚Äù
\v 2 Dughiar kam…®n Sol…®n adarazir ingangarir gumazir mam iti, an ziam Siba. Me atrivim…®n ganasa an dia, ez…® a ghua atrivim batoz…®ma atrivim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n ziam Siba?‚Äù
\p Ez…® a ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, gumazir ekiam, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazimra.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 9:3 \xt 2 Samuel 4:4\x*Ez…® atrivim Siban azara, ‚ÄúSol…®n adarazir tarazi ua ikiav…®ra iti o puvat…®? Tarazi ik…®t…®, k…® God…®n apangkuvir arazim men akakaghasa.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Siba kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúJonatan…®n otarir vam…®ra ikiav…®ra ikia, egha an dagarimning uaghara ikufi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® atrivim an azara, ‚ÄúA managh iti?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Siba a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúA Lodebar…®n nguibar ekiam…®n Amiel…®n otarim Makir…®n d…®penim…®n iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n oregha, gumazir maba amadaz…® me ghua Lodebar…®n nguibar ekiam…®n Amiel…®n otarim Makir…®n d…®penim…®n otogha otarir kam inigha izi.
\v 6 Otarir kam…®n ziam Mefiboset, a Jonatan…®n otarim egha Atrivim Sol…®n igiavotarim. A izav otogha, uan tevimning ap…®righa aviragha guam nguazim…®n m…®tua, egha ziar ekiam Devit gan…®ngi. Ez…® Devit an m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAruer aghuim, Mefiboset.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Mefiboset ghaze, ‚ÄúK…®rara, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazir k…®nim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Devit a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® n…®n afeziam Jonatan g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti. Egha a bang…®n k…® apangkuvir arazim…®n n…® damuam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® atiatingan mark…®. Egh n…® zurara nan d…®penim…®n iz…® na ko nan dagher dakozim…®n damam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Mefiboset ua uan tevimning ap…®righa aviragha, uan guam nguazim…®n m…®tuagha ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim, n…® bizir tizim bagh arazir aghuir kam…®n na damuasa? K…® pura bizir k…®nim. K…® mati afiar aremezir kuam…®n m…®n iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Egha Mefiboset ghugha g…®vaz…®, Atrivim Devit, Sol…®n ingangarir gumazim Siban diaz…® a izima, a kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n gumazir ekiam Sol uan adarazi ko, men nguaziba ko biziba bar, k…® da is…®va Mefiboset…®n dafarim dar…®gham. A Sol…®n igiavotarim.
\v 10 Eght…® n…® uan otariba ko ingangarir gumaziba ko, ia nguazir kam…®n azenibar ingar. Egh ia dagher azenibar dagher m…®t…®ghiziba asigh da inigh iz…®. Eght…® arazir kam…®n, n…®n gumazir ekiam…®n adarazi dagheba ikiam. Eght…® Mefiboset uab…®, zurara iz…® na ko nan dagher dakozim…®n damam.‚Äù Dughiar kam…®n, Siba 15plan otariba ikia 20plan ingangarir gumaziba iti.
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Siba kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim, n…®n nan gumazir ekiam, bizir n…® damuasa na m…®kemeziba, k…® bar dar amuam.‚Äù Bizir kam…®n g…®n, Mefiboset ghuava atrivim ko an dagher dakozim…®n api, egha mati atrivim…®n otarir mam.
\p 
\v 12 Mefiboset otarir igiar mam iti, an ziam Mika. Dughiar kam…®n, Siban d…®penim…®n itir adarazi ko an ingangarir gumazamiziba me bar, Mefiboset bagha ingangaribagh ami.
\v 13 Ez…® Mefiboset uab…® Jerusalem…®n ikia, zurara Atrivim Devit ko an dagher dakozim…®n apa a ko iti. Mefiboset…®n dagarimning uaghara ikufi.
\c 10
\ms1 Atrivim Devit…®n otaribar eghaghanim
\mr (Sapta 10--20)
\s1 Devit Amonia ko Siriaba ab…®ni
\r (1 Eghaghaniba 19:1-19)
\p 
\v 1 Bizir kam…®n g…®n, Amonian atrivim aremez…®, an otarim Hanun an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\v 2 Ez…® Devit ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® arazir aghuim…®n Hanun damuam, mati an afeziam Nahas faragha arazir aghuim…®n na gami.‚Äù
\p Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Devit apangkuvir m…®g…®r…®g…®abar Hanun…®n m…®k…®masa uan abuir gumazir maba amada. Ez…® me ghua otozir dughiam…®n,
\v 3 kantri Amonian gumazir dapaniba uan atrivim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ti ghaze, Devit abuir gumazir kaba amadaz…®, me ziar ekiam n…®n afeziam dan…®ngasa ize? Bar puvat…®. A me amadaz…® me modogh en nguibar ekiam getiva an ganasa oda ize. Egh me g…®n uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko iz…® e gas…®ghas…®gham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Hanun akar kam baregha, Devit…®n abuir gumazibar suigha, men ghuamas…®ziba vaghvagha dar vuebagh isegha vueba ataki. Egha uaghan men korotiar ruariba ar…®ghara da aghorez…® da bar otefe, ez…® men m…®tiarakaba azenimra iti. Egha me amadaz…® me ghue.
\v 5 Ez…® abuir gumazir kaba bar aghumsigha, uamategh uan nguibabar mangan aghua. Ez…® Devit Hanun amizir bizir kam baregha, kamagh…®n abuir gumazir kaba bagha akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Jerikon nguibar ekiamra ik…® mang…®t…® ian ghumas…®ziba uam otivigh g…®vaght…® ia Jerusalem…®n iz…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Amonia kamagh…®n fo, me Devit…®n gumazibagh amizir bizir kam bagh, a bar men an…®ngaghegham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me nguibar av…®rir kabar m…®dorozir gumaziba bagha akaba amangi. Egha me Sirian kantrin aven itir nguibar ekiamning, Betrehop ko Soban m…®dorozir gumazitaba iniasa, me ko akam ak…®rasa ghue. Ez…® me Amonian akurvaghasa 20,000plan m…®dorozir gumaziba amada. Ez…® me ua Top…®n nguibar ekiam…®n m…®dorozir gumazir 12,000pla ini. Egha me ua uarir akurvaghasa, 1,000plan m…®dorozir gumaziba bagha Makan atrivim ko akam ak…®ri.
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Devit orazi, Amonia uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me akufa. Egha a Joap ko m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me amadaz…®, me me ko m…®soghasa zui.
\v 8 Ez…® Amonia uan nguibar ekiam…®n azenan izegha m…®soghasa uari ar…®gha, d…®vazim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n tuivighav iti. Ez…® Siriaba ko Topia ko Makaba, me uarira dadar torim…®n tuivighav iti. Egha m…®soghasa uari ar…®gha iti.
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Joap apanir kabar ganigha fo, m…®dorozir gumazir okoruar pumuning, vong ko vong sara d…®kavigh iz…® a ko m…®sogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Israelian gumazir gavgavir deragha m…®sozir maba am…®sevegha me isa, dadar torim…®n itir apanir kabar arava b…®zim…®n me afe. Egha a uab…® men dapanim…®n ikia faragha tu.
\v 10 Egha a uan dozim Abisai am…®sevez…®, a m…®dorozir gumazir igharazibar faragha zui. Egha Amonian m…®dorozir gumazibar arava men borogh…®n uan m…®dorozir gumaziba b…®zim…®n me afa zui.
\v 11 Egha Joap kamagh…®n Abisai m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® gant…®, Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba e adugh mang…® e ab…®ns…® damut…®, ia iz…® en akuragh. Eght…® Amonia ia adugh mang…® ia ab…®ns…® damut…®, e mang…® ian akuragham.
\v 12 Ia atiatingan mark…®! E uan gumazamiziba ko nguibar ekiar God e gan…®ngiziba bagh n…®ghnigh pamtem…®n m…®sogham. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God damuasa ifongezir bizir aghuim a mar guizbang…®rama otogh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Egha Joap uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko Siriabav soghasa ghua garima, me ara tintinibar ghue.
\v 14 Ez…® Amonia gari, Siriaba arima, me uaghan Abisain adarazir damazim…®n ara ghua uan nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazir ekiam…®n aven monge. Ez…® Joap pura Amonia ategha uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghu.
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® Siriaba garima, Israelia m…®dorozim…®n me ab…®ra, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me uan m…®dorozir gumazibar diaz…®ma me bar iza uari akufa.
\v 16 Ez…® Atrivim Hadateser gumazir maba amangiz…®, me ghua Yufretis…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n otogha, Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha ghua bar Helam…®n nguibar ekiam…®n me akufa. Ez…® Atrivim Hadateser…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir dapanim Sobak, men faragha ghua men gumazir dapanim…®n iti.
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® Devit orazi, Siriaba iza Helam…®n uari akuvagha itima, a Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me inigha ghua Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gha vong…®n ghua Helam…®n ghu. Ez…® Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba tuiva m…®soghasa uari ar…®gha magh…®ra Israelia ko m…®dorozim fore.
\v 18 Ez…® Israelian m…®dorozim bar gavgavigha Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba adugha zuima me are. Ez…® Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, men 700plan karisbagh is…®n ikia m…®sozir gumaziba ko 40,000plan nguazim…®n tuiva m…®sozir gumazibav soghez…®, me ariaghire. Egha uaghan Sirian m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim Sobak m…®soghez…®ma, a danganir kamrama areme.
\v 19 Ez…® Atrivim Hadateser…®n apengan itir atrivir maba garima, Israelia me ab…®nigha g…®fa. Ez…® me tagha, Israelia ko navir vam…®ran ikiasa akam ak…®righa Israelian apengan iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Siriaba uam Amonian akurvazir puvat…®.
\c 11
\s1 Devit Urian amuim ko arazir kuram gami
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 11:1 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 20:1\x*Ez…® azeniba vaghvagha, dar dughiar orangt…®ziba g…®vasava amima, atriviba uan m…®dorozir gumaziba isa uan apaniba ko m…®soghasa zui. Ez…® Devit Amonia m…®soghasa Joap ko, uan m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapaniba ko Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba, a bar me amangi. Ez…® me ghua Amonia m…®sogha me ab…®ragha, Raban nguibar ekiam…®n m…®dorozim fore. Ez…® Devit uab…® m…®dorozim bagha ghuzir puvat…®gha Jerusalemra iti.
\p 
\v 2 Egha guarat…®zir mam…®n aruem uaghira bar m…®gorima, Devit uan m…®siam…®n d…®kavigha avughsa uan d…®penim…®n p…®n itir danganim garui. Egha garima amizir mam uan d…®penim…®n rua iti. Amizir kam, an ganganiba bar dera.
\v 3 Ez…® Devit foghasa, munar amizir manamra rue, egha gumazir mam amadaz…®ma a foghasa ghu. Ez…® gumazim ghua an ganigha kamagh…®n fo, kar Batseba, Eliam…®n guivim. A Hitian adarazir gumazir mam Uria, an amuim.
\v 4 Ez…® Devit gumazir maba amangiz…® me ghua Batseba inigha ize. Dughiar kam…®n, Batseba uan iak…®nibav suegha g…®vagha, uan m…®karzim zuasa bizibagh ami. Egha Batseba Devit bagha izez…®, Devit a koma akuiz…®, Batseba g…®n uamategha uan d…®penim…®n ghu.
\v 5 Egha g…®n Batseba borim…®n duirava fo, a navim adai, egha Devit bagha akam amada.
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Devit oregha Joap bagha akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® Hitian gumazim Uria amadaght…® a na bagh izegh.‚Äù Ez…® Joap Devit bagha Uria amadaz…®, a ize.
\p 
\v 7 Uria Devit bagha izez…®, a kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúJoap deraz…® an m…®dorozir gumaziba uaghan dera? Ez…® m…®dorozim manmagh…®ra zui? Me, en apaniba ab…®nigham, o?‚Äù Ez…® Uria m…®dorozim…®n otivizir biziba bar a geghani.
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Devit Urian m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúBar dera, k…® oregha g…®fa. N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n uan d…®penim…®n mang…® dagarimning ruegh avughs…®.‚Äù Ez…® Uria Atrivim Devit ategha azenan ghuz…®, Devit g…®n bizir aghuir maba Uria dan…®ngasa, da isa gumazir mam gan…®ngiz…® an ada inigha a bagha zui.
\v 9 Ez…® Uria uan d…®penim…®n ghuzir puvat…®. A uan gumazir ekiam…®n gumazir a geghuviba ko, me atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n tiar akar m…®riam…®n akui.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Devit orazi, Uria uan d…®penim…®n ghuzir puvat…®z…®, Devit ghuava a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha uan d…®penim…®n ghuzir puvat…®? N…® dughiar ruarim…®n m…®dorozim…®n ikia uan d…®penim…®n ikezir puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Uria kamagh…®n Devit ikara, ‚ÄúIsraelia ko Judabar m…®dorzir gumaziba m…®dorozir danganimra iti. Ez…® Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam me ko ikiav…®ra iti. Ez…® nan gumazir ekiam Joap, m…®dorozir gumaziba ko pura danganir azentuzim…®n averpenibar ikiav…®ra iti. Eght…® k…® uab…®ra mang…® uan d…®penim…®n deragh dam…®va, d…®pabar am…®, egh uan amuim ko dakut…®, kamagh…®n bar deraghan kogham. K…® bar guizbang…®ra arazir katam damighan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Devit a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n kagh ikeght…® k…® gurumzaraghan, ua n…® amadaght…® n…® mangam.‚Äù Ez…® aruer kam…®n Uria Jerusalem…®n iti. Ez…® am…®mzaraghan guarat…®gh…®n,
\v 13 Devit Urian diaz…® a iza a ko apima, a d…®par onganiba a gan…®ngiz…® an ada amegha bar ongani. Egha d…®magarir kam…®n, Uria dakuasa uan d…®penim…®n iraghuzir puvat…®. A uan daguivsiam ghuaragha, gumazir atrivim geghuva itiba koma akui.
\p 
\v 14 Egha am…®mzaraghan, Devit Joap bagha ak…®nafarir mam osirigha, Uria gan…®ngigha anemadaz…®ma a uamategha m…®dorozir danganim…®n ghu.
\v 15 Devit kamagh…®n ak…®nafarim osiri, ‚ÄúN…® Uria is…® m…®dorozim bar gavgaviz…® nagh…®n anet…®gh. Egh ia bar uari am…®k…®rvegh g…®rak…®rang…®n izeght…®, apaniba a m…®sueght…® an aremegh.‚Äù
\v 16 Dughiar kam…®n Joap m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me Raban nguibar ekiam iniasa m…®soghav…®ra iti. Egha Joap ak…®nafarim inigha g…®vagha egha gari, Amonian m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba bar pamten m…®sozir danganim, a Uria isava danganir kam…®n anet…®.
\v 17 Ez…® Amonian m…®dorozir gumaziba uan nguibar ekiam av…®nasa azenan iza, Joap…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ko m…®sosi. Ez…® m…®dorozir kam…®n aven, Devit…®n ingangarir gumazir dapanir maba ariaghire, ez…® Uria uaghan me koma areme.
\p 
\v 18 Joap g…®n Devit bagha akam amaga m…®dorozir kam…®n otivizir bizibar gun m…®gei.
\v 19 Egha Joap gumazir akar kaba inigh mangamim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúM…®dorozir kam…®n aven otivizir biziba n…® bar adar gun Devit…®n m…®kemegh.
\v 20 Eght…® an atar kamagh…®n n…® m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòIa manmaghsua ghua nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazim bar an m…®riamra ghugha m…®sosi? Ia kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, apaniba d…®vazim gis…®n tuivigh ik…®va, barir pibar ia gasegham.
\v 21 \x - \xo 11:21 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 9:53\x*Ia ti fom…®ra Gideon…®n otarim Abimelek batozir bizir kam bak…®n…®gh…®nigha mati? Gideon…®n otarim Abimelek, a fom…®ra Tebes…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n d…®vazir m…®riam…®n tughav itima, amizir mam d…®vazim gis…®n ikia, dag…®ar wit m…®rm…®rir mam puegha a m…®k…®niz…® an areme. Ez…® ia manmaghsua bar d…®vazir m…®riam…®n borogh…®n ghue?‚Äô Atrivim m…®kemegh g…®vaght…®, n…® kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòN…®n Ingangarir Gumazim Uria, Hitian gumazim, a uaghan areme.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® gumazir kam Joap…®n akaba inigha Devit bagha ize.
\v 23 Egha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúApaniba gavgavigha e adugha nguibar ekiam…®n azenan izegha tuzir torim…®n e m…®sosi. Ez…® e ua me adugha bar ghua nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akam…®n ghu.
\v 24 Ez…® Amonian m…®dorozir gumazir maba d…®vazir ekiam…®n p…®n ikia, barir pibar n…®n ingangaribar garir gumazir dapanir mabagh asez…® me ariaghire. Ez…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim Uria, a Hitian gumazim, a uaghan areme.‚Äù
\p 
\v 25 Ez…® Devit a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® uamategh mang…® Joap…®n m…®k…®m suam, A m…®dorozim…®n aven otivizir bizibagh n…®ghnigh, egh da bagh pamtem…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Gumazitam foghan kogham, tinara m…®dorozim…®n aven ovegham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an Amonia m…®sogh me ab…®nigh, egh men nguibar ekiam bar a gas…®ghas…®kigh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® Batseba g…®n uan pam…®n ovevem baregha, a bagh azia iti.
\v 27 \x - \xo 11:27 \xt Onger Akaba 51:4\x*A uan pam g…®bua a bagha ikegha g…®vaz…®ma, Devit gumazir mabav kemez…® me Batseban akua a bagha atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n ize. Ez…® Devit an itima, an otarir mam bate. Ez…® Devit amizir arazir kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar a gifongezir puvat…®.
\c 12
\s1 Natan Devit…®n arazir kuram aghuri
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 12:1 \xt Onger Akaba 51:1\x*Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Devit bagha uan akam inigha izir gumazim Natan amada. Ez…® Natan iza a batogha kamagh…®n Devit geghari, ‚ÄúDughiar mam gumazir pumuning nguibar ekiar mam…®n iti. Aning…®n mav bizir av…®riba iti, ez…® mav onganarazibagh amua bizir av…®riba puvat…®.
\v 2 Gumazir bizir av…®riba itim, a bulmakauba ko sipsip…®n bar av…®riba iti.
\v 3 Ez…® gumazir biziba puvat…®zim, sipsip…®n nguzir amebar vam…®ra ua bagha a givezegha an akuaghapi, ez…® an a ko iti. Egha a deraghav…®ra sipsip…®n nguzir amebar kam…®n garima, an an boriba ko d…®penim…®n ikia ghuava ekefe. A dagher muziarir a itiba, ana da ab…®gha dar naba isa uan sipsip gan…®ga anetagh…®razima, a an d…®paba apir kav…®n d…®par naba api. Egha an a isa uan evarim gar…®gha a muagha akui. Ez…® sipsip…®n kam mati an guivim…®n m…®raram oto.
\v 4 Ez…® dughiar mam…®n, gumazir mam iza gumazir bizir av…®riba itim…®n d…®penim…®n ize. Ez…® a uan namakar a bagha izezim bagh uan sipsip…®n tam o bulmakaun tam m…®suegh a bagh isaman aghua. Egha a gumazir biziba puvat…®zim…®n sipsip…®n nguzim okemegha a m…®suegha uan namakar a bagha izezim bagha a isami.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n oregha, gumazir bizir av…®riba itir kam bar a basemegha, kamagh…®n Natan m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n guizbang…®ra m…®gei, gumazir arazir kurar kam gamizim, me a m…®sueght…®, an aremeght…® deragham.
\v 6 Guizbang…®ra, a gumazir biziba puvat…®zim…®n apangkuvir puvat…®gha arazir bar kuram gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a 4plan sipsipba is…®, a inizir sipsip…®n kam ikarvagham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Natan kamagh…®n Devit m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…®rara, gumazir k…® egharir kamnang! Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, a kamagh…®n n…® m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® n…®n akuraz…®, Sol n…® gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. K…® borem isa n…® gingegha n…® am…®sevez…®, n…® Israelian atrivim…®n oto.
\v 8 N…®n gumazir aruam Sol, k…® an d…®penim ko an biziba ko an amuiba, k…® bar da isa n…®n dafarim gat…®. Egha k…® n…® gamiz…® n…® Israelia ko Judabar atrivim…®n oto. Bizir kaba n…®n damazim…®n oteveght…®, k…® bizitaba ua n…® dan…®ngv…®ra ikiam.
\v 9 Ez…® n…® manmaghsua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam batuegha, an damazim…®n arazir kurar kam gami? N…® Hitian gumazim Uria m…®soghez…® an areme. N…® m…®dorozim bagha anemadaz…®, Amonia uan m…®dorozir sabam…®n a m…®soghez…® an areme, ez…® n…® an amuim ini.
\v 10 Ez…® n…® deraghv…®ram oragh. N…® nan akam batuegha Urian amuim…®n ikiasava a ini. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dughiar g…®n izibar, gumaziba n…®n ovavir borir tabav soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiram, eght…® arazir kam ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äô
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 12:11-12 \xt 2 Samuel 16:22\x*‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, K…® n…®n adarazir gumazitabar amight…®, me os…®mt…®zir ekiaba n…® dar…®gham. Egh n…®n damazim…®n, k…® n…®n amuiba is…® gumazir igharazibar an…®ngam. Eght…® me azenara arazir kurabar n…®n amuibar amuam.
\v 12 N…® uan arazir kuram modogha a gami, ez…® k…® n…®n arazir kurar kam, azenara a ikarvaght…®, Israelia bar an ganam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n oregha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kuram gami.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Natan a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amada, ez…® n…® aremeghan kogham.
\v 14 Ez…® n…®n arazir kurar kam bang…®n, apaniba akar kurabar Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…®n otarir Batseba otezim aremegham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Natan Devit…®n arazir kurabar gun a m…®kemegha g…®vagha, uamategha uan d…®penim…®n ghu.
\p Ez…® g…®n, Devit…®n borim, Ikiav…®ra Itir God a gamiz…®, a puv…®ram arei.
\s1 Devit…®n otarim areme
\p 
\v 16 Devit…®n otarim arei, ez…® otarim ghuamaghasa, Devit dagheba tagha God ko m…®g…®a a gaghori. A d…®magaribar uan d…®penim…®n ghua pura nguazim girav iti.
\v 17 Ez…® an ingangarir gumazir aruaba ghua an m…®riam…®n tuivigha egha d…®kavasa a m…®geima, a me barazir puvat…®. A uaghan me ko daman aghua.
\v 18 Ez…® 7plan dughiaba g…®vaz…®ma, an borim areme, ez…® an ingangarir gumaziba an borim…®n ovevem…®n gun an m…®k…®man bar atiatingi. Me kamagh…®n uarira uariv gei, ‚ÄúBorim t…®ghar ovengamin dughiam…®n, e a m…®geima an e barazi puvat…®. Kamagh…®n e dat…®r…®gh…®n borim…®n ovevem…®n gun a m…®kemeghan kogham. A bizir kam baregh ti d…®kavigh uab…® gas…®ghasigham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® Devit garima, an ingangarir gumaziba sighsirir akabar uarira uariv geima a fo, borim ti aremegha g…®fa. Ez…® a men azara, ‚ÄúBorim aremez, o?‚Äù
\p Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, an areme.‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Egha Devit akar kam baregha, nguazim…®n d…®kavigha ghua rue. Egha borem uan m…®karzim gaghuigha, korotiar aghuiba aghuigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fasa an D…®penim…®n ghua, uan tevimning ap…®righa dapanim aviragha guam nguazim m…®tua. Egha Devit ua uan d…®penim…®n izegha, dagheba isair gumazibav m…®kemez…®, me a bagha dagher maba tuigha a gan…®ngiz…®, ana da api.
\v 21 Devit arazir kam gamiz…®ma, ingangarir gumaziba kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® arazir manmagh…®n amizim gami? N…®n borim aremezir puvat…®zir dughiam…®n, n…® a bagha aziava dagheba ta. Ez…® borim aremez…®, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®kavigha dagheba api. N…® m…®ngarir manam gatava arazir kam gami?‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Devit me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ghaze, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ti nan apangkuvigh nan borim damight…® an aremeghan kogham. Kamagh…®n borim angam…®ra ikiav…®ra itima, k…® aziava dagheba ta.
\v 23 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n an aremegha g…®vaz…®, k…® tizim bagh dagheba tagham? Arazir kam…®n k…® ua borim damight…® a d…®kavigh angam…®ra ikiam? Bar puvat…®. A zuir danganir kam k…® g…®n uaghan an mangam. Egh a ua na bagh izeghan kogham.‚Äù
\s1 Batseba Solomon bate
\p 
\v 24 Egha g…®n Devit gavgavim uan amuim Batseba dan…®ngasa, akar aghuibar a m…®gei. Egha Devit a koma akuiz…®ma, a navim asegha otarir igharazir mam bate. Ez…® Devit ziam Solomon a gat…®. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar borir kam gifonge.
\v 25 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® ziar kam Jedidia\f + \fr 12:25 \ft Ziar kam Jedidia, an m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God bar a gifonge.‚Äù\f* borim dar…®ghasa, uan akam inigha izir gumazim Natan amadaz…® a Devit bagha ghu.
\s1 Devit m…®sogha Raban nguibar ekiam ini
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Joap uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, Raban nguibar ekiam…®n m…®sogha ghuav…®ra iti, kar Amonian atrivim…®n nguibar ekiam. Egha me nguibar ekiar kam…®n akuar mam ini.
\v 27 Egha a Devit bagha akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Raban nguibam ko m…®sogha men d…®paba tuir danganim inigha g…®fa.
\v 28 Eght…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, n…® zuam…®ra Israel…®n m…®dorozir gumazir ikiav…®ra itiba akuvagh, me amadaght…®, me iz…® pamtem…®n Raban gumaziba ko m…®sogh me ab…®nigh…®va nguibar ekiam inigh. Puvat…®ght…®, nan adarazira m…®sogh me ab…®night…®, gumazamiziba nan ziam nguibar ekiar kam dar…®gham.‚Äù
\v 29 Ez…® Devit akar kam inigha g…®vagha, m…®dorozir gumazir ikiav…®ra itiba akuvagha, me bar ghua Raban gumaziba ko m…®sogha me ab…®nigha nguibar ekiam ini.
\v 30 Egha Devit Amonian atrivim…®n dapanir asuam ini. Dapanir asuar kam, me gol…®n an ingariz…®, an os…®mt…®zim 35 kilogrem. Dapanir asuar kam, me dag…®ar dirir bar p…®n kozir mam…®n an kuruke. Ez…® Israelia dapanir asuar kam inigha Devit…®n dapanim garu. Devit uaghan dag…®aba ko bizir aghuir av…®riba nguibar ekiar kam…®n ada ini.
\v 31 Egha Devit Raban nguibar ekiam…®n itir gumazamiziba bar me inigha, ingangarir guar av…®ribar amuasa me ar…®si. Marazi sobiar ingarir ingangaribagh ami, marazi ain…®n afavibar ingangaribagh ami, marazi ain…®n sobiabar ingangaribagh ami. Ez…® marazi brighbar ingari.\f + \fr 12:31 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Gumazir maba ghaze, a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEgha a Raban nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamiziba bar me inigha egha soba ko ain…®n afaviba ko ain…®n sobiabar me m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire. Egha a marazi brighbar ingarir aven…®n marazi tue.‚Äù\f* Arazir kamra, Devit kantri Amon…®n nguibar ekiar igharaziba bar men gumazamizibagh ami. Egha g…®n, Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghue.
\c 13
\s1 Amnon arazir kuram…®n Tamar gami
\p 
\v 1 Bizir kam…®n g…®rara, arazir mam oto. Devit…®n otarim Apsalom, a buaramizir mam iti, an ziam Tamar. An ganganiba bar dera. Ez…® Devit…®n otarir igharazir mam, an ziam Amnon, amebar igharazim a bate. A bar Tamar gifongegha, a bagha navim d…®kafi.
\v 2 Tamar tong bar gumazitam koma akuigha fozir puvat…®z…®, me bar deragha a geghuvima a iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Amnon Tamar…®n borogh…®n mangamin tuaviba puvat…®, egha a zurara a g…®n…®ghn…®gha arei mogh…®n iti.
\v 3 Egha Amnon namakar mam iti, an ziam Jonadap. A Devit…®n avebam Saman otarim, a bizibav k…®mt…®, dar dagheba guizbang…®rama otivamin fofozir ekiam iti.
\v 4 Egha a Amnon…®n azara, ‚ÄúAtrivim…®n otarim, n…® na m…®k…®m, manmagh…®n amiz…® k…® zurara n…®n garima, n…® osemegha arei mogh…®n gari?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Amnon a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® uan avebam Apsalom…®n buaramizim Tamar, bar a gifonge.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Jonadap a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ifar arei mogh…®n damu, egh uan m…®siam…®n ir…®gh…®v ik…® mamagh…®ra ik…®. Eght…® n…®n afeziam n…®n gans…® aven iz…®t…®, n…® kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòGa uaning! N…® nan buaramizim Tamar amadaght…® an aven iz…®, eght…® k…® gant…®, a na bagh daghetam tuam. Egh a uab…® daghem na dan…®ngt…® k…® aneremam.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Amnon, Jonadap…®n akam baregha, ghua uan m…®siam…®n ghugha ifara arei mogh…®n amua uan m…®siam gir…®ghav iti. Ez…® Atrivim Devit an ar…®mariar akam baregha an ganasa an d…®penim…®n ghu. Ez…® Amnon a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGa uaning! K…® ar…®a n…®n azangs…®si, n…® nan buaramizim Tamar amadaght…® an aven iz…®, eght…® k…® gant…® a na bagh kek…®n taba tu. Egh a uab…® kek…®n kaba inigh na dan…®ngt…® k…® dar amam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Dughiar kam…®n, Tamar atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n itima, Devit a bagha akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® uan tuebam Amnon…®n d…®penim…®n mang…®va a bagh daghetam tuam.‚Äù
\v 8 Ez…® Tamar oregha uan tuebam Amnon…®n d…®penim…®n ghugha garima, a uan m…®siam gir…®ghav iti. A ir…®ghav ikia garima, Tamar plauan maba inigha plaua giragha kekba tuer m…®nem…®n da tue.
\p 
\v 9 A kekba tuer m…®nem isa kekba Amnon…®n damazim…®n da ingegha itarim gat…®. Ez…® Amnon daman aghua. Egha a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa ingarir gumaziba bar, ia azenan mang…®.‚Äù Ez…® gumazamiziba kamagh…®n oregha, me bar d…®penim ategha azenan ghue.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Amnon Tamar m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® kekba inigh k…® akui nagh…®n iz…®, egh kekba is…® na dan…®ngt…® k…® dar amam.‚Äù Ez…® Tamar kek…®n tuezir kaba inigha a ir…®ghav iti nagh…®n a bagha zui.
\p 
\v 11 Tamar kekba inigha ghuava Amnon dan…®ngasa amima, a magh…®ra an dafarim gitorogha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNan buaramizim, n…® iz…® nan m…®siam…®n na ko dakuasa k…® ifonge.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Tamar a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúMarkiam, n…® nan tuebam. N…® arazir kurar kam damus…® na gaghonan mark…®. E Israelia arazir kurar kabagh amir puvat…®. N…® aghums…®zir arazir m…®z…®r…®zir kam damuan mark…®.
\v 13 N…® arazir kurar kam damight…®, k…® aghums…®zir ekiam inigh, ua gumazamizibar damazim…®n daruan kogham. Eght…® Israelia bar m…®k…®m suam, n…® bar ikufi, egh me n…® d…®pova bar paz…®v…®ra n…® m…®k…®m…®va bar n…® ab…®ragham. Ga uaning! N…® arazir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n a damus…® n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. N…® nan ik…®s…® ifuegh, ga uan afeziam Atrivim Devit…®n azaraka. N…® nan ik…®s…®, a ti n…®n amamangat…®gham.‚Äù
\v 14 Ez…® Amnon Tamar…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am baraghan aghuagha, uan gavgavim sarama an suiragha, a gekuigha a gakaghora a koma akui.
\p 
\v 15 Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n a Tamar…®n aghua. A faragha bar Tamar gifonge, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n bar a basemegha bar an aghua. An an aghuazir arazim bar ekevegha, a faragha a gifongezir arazim gafira. Egha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh na gitagh mang…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Tamar a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúNan tuebam, n…® na barakigh. N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n na batogha na gamir arazir kurar kam, a n…® nan suiragha arazir kuram…®n na gamizir arazim bar a gafiragham.‚Äù Ez…® Amnon bar tong Tamar barazir puvat…®.
\v 17 Egha uan ingangarir gumazir igiam…®n diagha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® iz…® amizir kam nan damazim…®n a batueght…® an azenan mang…®t…®, n…® tiam asaragh.‚Äù
\v 18 (Dughiar kam…®n, Tamar korotiar ruarir kurkazir bar aghuiba itiba arugha, Amnon bagha ghu. Kar atrivibar guivir t…®ghar pam…®n ikiamiba azuir korotiar aghuir ruariba.) Ez…® Amnon…®n ingangarir gumazim a batoghez…® an azenim gir…®z…®, a tiam asara.
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® Tamar uan navir os…®mt…®zim akakagha, averenim uan dapanim gaghuigha korotiar ruarir kam ab…®ki. Egha dafarimning uan dapanim gat…®gha, pamten aziav…®ra zui.
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® Apsalom uan buaramizim Tamar…®n garima, an aziav…®ra izima, a an azara, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n ami? N…®n tuebam Amnon n…® ko akua arazitam…®n n…® gamiz…® n…® azia izi? Amnon, a n…®n tuebam, kamagh…®n, n…® azir akam ategh pura uab…® am…®ragh m…®gh…®gh bizir a n…® gamizir kam…®n os…®man mark…®. Egh n…®n tuebam Amnon n…® gamizir arazir kurar kam…®n gun gumazitam m…®k…®man mark…®.‚Äù Ez…® Tamar Apsalom…®n d…®penim…®n ghugha a ko iti, ez…® os…®mt…®zir kam zurarama aneb…®rav…®ra iti.
\v 21 Ez…® Atrivim Devit eghaghanir kam baregha an muriam bar mogh…®ra ikufi.\f + \fr 13:21 \ft Bar fom…®ra gumaziba Hibrun akam, me Grigh…®n akam…®n a g…®ra, egha vez…®n kam…®n me mong an ruarim osiri. Ez…® e dat…®r…®gh…®n fozir puvat…®, me uari akar kam osiri, egha a fom…®ra Hibrun kam…®n iti, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n ua itir puvat…®. Grigh…®n akam ghaze, ‚ÄúAmnon Devit…®n otarir ivariam, ez…® Devit bar a gifonge. Kamagh…®n Devit Amnon ivezir kuram a gan…®ngizir puvat…®.‚Äù\f*
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Apsalom bizitam…®n bar Amnon m…®geir puvat…®gha bar aghumra iti. Amnon an buaramizim suiragha a gekuigha ghua arazir kuram…®n a gami, kamagh…®n amiz…®, Apsalom bar an an…®ngaghegha an aghua.
\s1 Apsalom, Amnon m…®sueght…® // an aremeghasa tuaviba buri
\p 
\v 23 Azenir pumuning g…®vaz…®ma, Apsalom uan ingangarir gumaziba ko Balhasor…®n nguibam…®n sipsip…®n ar…®zibagh is…®, isam damuasa atrivibar otariba bagha bar akaba amangi. Nguibar kam a Efraim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n iti.
\v 24 Egha Apsalom Atrivim Devit bagha ghua, kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, ga uaning. K…® uan gumaziba ko sipsip…®n ar…®zibagh is…® isam damuasa. Egh n…® uan ingangarir gumazir dapaniba ko, ia nan isam…®n izasa k…® ian azangs…®si.‚Äù
\p 
\v 25 Ez…® Atrivim Devit a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúNan otarim, ti puvat…®gham. E bar mangegh uam os…®mt…®zim n…® danigham.‚Äù Ez…® Apsalom mangasa a gaghorav…®ra iti. Ez…® atrivim an g…®n mangan aghuagha ghaze, Apsalom n…® mang…®, n…®n biziba deragham.
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® Apsalom a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa mamagh…®n izan aghuagh…®va, nan aveghbuam Amnon amadaght…®, an e bagh iz…®.‚Äù
\p Ez…® atrivim a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúA bizir tizim baghv…®ra n…®n g…®n mangam?‚Äù
\v 27 Ez…® Apsalom Amnon bagha Devit…®n azangs…®ghav…®ra iti, ez…® an Amnon ko uan otarir igharaziba saram amamangat…®z…®, me bar Apsalom…®n g…®n ghu.
\p 
\v 28 Egha me ghua Balhasor…®n nguibam…®n otivigha, Apsalom uan ingangarir gumaziba pamten me ab…®ra me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa isam…®n torim…®n gant…®, Amnon d…®par onganiba amegh onganight…®, k…® m…®k…®mv…®ra ik…®t…®, ia a m…®sueght…® a ir…®gh aremegh. K…® uab…® a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa ia m…®g…®a ia ab…®ra. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia tuivigh gavgavigh bizitam…®n atiatingan mark…®.‚Äù
\v 29 Ez…® Apsalom…®n ingangarir gumaziba a m…®kemez…® mogh…®rama isam…®n aven Amnon gamiz…®, Atrivim Devit…®n otarir igharaziba kamagh…®n ganigha d…®kavigha vaghvagha uan donkibagh apiagha bar puv are.
\p 
\v 30 Me tuavim…®n ghuav…®ra itima, gumazir mam men faragha ghua, Devit m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúApsalom n…®n otariba bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire, men tav itir puvat…®.‚Äù
\v 31 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n oregha d…®kavigha tugha uan korotiar ruarim abigha nguazim gir…®ghav ti. Ez…® an ingangarir gumaziba uaghan tuivighav…®ra ikia uan korotiar ruariba ab…®aghar…®si.
\p 
\v 32 Ez…® Devit…®n aveghbuam Sama, an otarim Jonadap kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan gumazir ekiam, n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim akar kabar ikian mark…®. Me n…®n otariba bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghirezir puvat…®. Me Amnonra m…®soghez…® an areme. Bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, Amnon faragha arazir kurabar Apsalom…®n buaramizim Tamar gami. Ez…® Apsalom zurara dughiabar bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra ikia, Amnon m…®soghez…® an areme. K…® Apsalom…®n guam…®n garima a m…®tarmangiz…®, k…® an n…®ghn…®zim g…®fo.\f + \fr 13:32 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\v 33 Atrivim, nan gumazir ekiam. N…® akar kaba is…® uan navir averiam dar…®ghan mark…®, kar pura akar k…®niba, n…®n otarir igharaziba ariaghirezir puvat…®. Amnon uab…®ram areme.‚Äù
\p 
\v 34-36 Ez…® Apsalom zuam…®ram arav ghu.
\p Jonadap Devit ko m…®g…®av…®ra itima, nguibar ekiam geghuva an garir m…®dorozir gumazir igiar mam, munagh…®ra Horonaim…®n izir tuavm…®n garima, gumazir av…®rim m…®ghs…®ar m…®riam…®n otivigha izaghiri. Ez…® an atrivim bagha ghua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® gumazir mabar garima me Horonaim…®n izir tuavm…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n m…®riam…®n otivigha izaghiri.‚Äù\f + \fr 13:34-36 \ft Vez…®n kam…®n aven, akar kam, ‚ÄúEz…® an atrivim bagha ghua kamagh a m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® gumazir mabar garima me Horonaim…®n izir tuavm…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n m…®riam…®n otivigha izaghiri,‚Äô ‚Äù a dat…®r…®gh…®n Hibrun akam…®n itir puvat…®. Akar kam ti fom…®ra ike, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n ovenge. Bar fom…®ra dughiar akam ikiav…®ra itim…®n, gumaziba Grik…®n akam…®n a g…®ra, ez…® akar kam a Grik…®n akam…®n ikiav…®ra iti.\f*
\p Ez…® Jonadap Devit m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® gan! K…® n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra mar atrivim…®n otaribara izi.‚Äù Jonadap m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, Devit…®n otariba aven izegha magh…®rama azi. Ez…® Devit uan ingangarir gumaziba ko, me me ko puv…®rama azi.
\s1 Apsalom arav ghu
\p 
\v 37-39 Apsalom ara ghua kantri Gesur…®n ikia, Atrivim Talmai ko iti. Talmai, a Amihut…®n otarim.\f + \fr 13:37-39 \ft Talmai an Apsalom…®n inazir afeziam. N…® 2 Samuel 3:3…®n gan.\f* An azenir 3plan Gesur…®n iti.
\p Ez…® Atrivim Devit dughiar ruarim…®n Amnon g…®bua a bagha ikegha g…®vagha, ua Apsalom…®n apangkuvigha ghaze, a uamategh iz…®.
\c 14
\s1 Apsalom ua izasa, Joap a bagha tuaviba buri
\p 
\v 1 Seruian otarim Joap kamagh…®n fo, Atrivim Devit…®n navim bar Apsalom baghav…®ra iti.
\v 2 Ez…® Joap amizir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itim bagha uan ingangarir gumazir mam amadaz…®, a ghua Tekoan nguibam…®n a inigha ize. Ez…® Joap kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n damuasa k…® ifonge, n…® ifar mati gumazim aremez…® n…® aghuimazim…®n iti mogh…®n ik…®. N…® aghuimazir korotiabar aghuigh, egh borem uan m…®karzim daghuan mark…®. N…® mati gumazim aremez…® n…® dughiar ruarim…®n a g…®bua iti mogh…®n ik…®.
\v 3 Egh n…® atrivim bagh mang…®va akar k…® n…® gan…®dir kabar gun a m…®k…®m.‚Äù Egha Joap atrivim m…®k…®mamin akabar amizim m…®gei.
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Tekoan amizir kam atrivim bagha ghugha, atrivim…®n damazim…®n nguazim gir…®gha uan guam nguazim m…®tuagha, ziar ekiam a gan…®ga ghaze, ‚ÄúO atrivim, n…® nan akuragh.‚Äù
