\p Ez…® amizim ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim, guizbang…®ra, nan pam aremez…® k…® odiarim…®n iti.
\v 6 K…® n…®n ingangarir amizim. K…® faragha otarir pumuningra iti. Egha aning azenibar ikia uaning…®n atara uaning m…®sozima, aning…®n tong…®n m…®dorozim ab…®ghan gumaziba puvat…®. Ez…® mav mav…®n m…®soghez…® an areme.
\v 7 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n nan pam…®n ik…®zim…®n adarazi bar d…®kavigha nan atara ghaze, otarir uan aveghbuam m…®soghez…® an aremezim, n…® a is…® en dafarim dat…®ght…®, e a m…®sueght…® an aremegh, uan aveghbuam…®n ovevem ikaragham. K…® men akam…®n g…®n mang…®va, k…® otariba puvat…®gham. Mati k…® avivk…®ar mam iti, ez…® me anemungasa. Me kamagh…®n damight…®, nan pam ko an ik…®zim…®n ziam nguazir kam…®n ikian kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Atrivim Devit, amizim…®n akam baregha kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, k…® n…®n os…®mt…®zim n…® bagh anek…®ram. N…® uamategh uan d…®penim…®n mang…®.‚Äù
