\v 10 Ez…® atrivim a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazitam m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kuratam n…® m…®kemeght…®, n…® a inigh na bagh iz…®t…®, k…® a m…®kemeght…® a ua kamagh…®n n…® damuan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® amizim ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGa uaning, atrivim, k…® kamagh…®n ifonge, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a n…®n God, n…® an ziam…®n m…®ghv…®ra a m…®k…®mt…®ma, me nan otarir igharazim m…®sueght…® an aremeghan mark…®. Bar markiam. Guizbang…®ra, en arazim kamak…®n, gumazim uan aveghbuam m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, gumazir kam…®n anababara a m…®sueght…® an aremegham. Ez…® n…® arazir kam…®n g…®n mangan mark…®, eght…® gumazitam nan otarim m…®sueght…® an aremeghan mark…®.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Devit ghaze, ‚ÄúK…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, n…®n otarim…®n dapanir ar…®zitam tong nguazim gir…®ghan kogham. An aremeghan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® amizim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGa uaning, nan atrivir ekiam, k…® n…®n ingangarir amizir k…®nim. N…® na ateght…® k…® tong ua m…®kemeka?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Devit ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera n…® m…®k…®m.‚Äù
