\v 13 Ez…® amizim kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha bizir kurar kam…®n God…®n gumazamizibagh ami? N…® uab…® uan otarim batuegha anetaghiz…®, a ua izezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, akar n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n na m…®kemezir kam, n…® uab…® uab…® isa kotiam gat…®.
\v 14 E fo, e bar mogh…®ra ar…®ghiregh ua angam…®ra ikian kogham, mati gumazim d…®pam nguazim gingeght…®, gumazitam uam a iniva avegham. God pura gumazibar ik…®r…®m…®riba agevir puvat…®. Eght…® gumazitam an saghon ik…®t…®ma, a gumazir kam inigh uab…®n borogh…®n iz…®s…®, a bagh tuaviba buriam.
\v 15 Atrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, ga uaning, gumazamiziba na gas…®ghas…®ghasa na m…®gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® men atiatia, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® m…®k…®masa n…® bagha izi. K…® n…®n ingangarir amizim, k…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, k…® n…®n azaraght…®ma, n…® nan akurvaghamin tuavitam batogham.
\v 16 K…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, gumazir maba k…® uan otarim ko, ga gas…®ghas…®ghava ami, eght…® God ga gan…®ngizir nguazir kam, ga an ikian kogham. K…® ghaze, n…® ti nan akam baragh nan akuragh, gumazir kabar dafarim da ua ga iniam.
\v 17 \x - \xo 14:17 \xt 2 Samuel 19:27\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ghaze, n…® na bagh akar gavgavitam ak…®right…® k…® deraghv…®ra ikiam. Atrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, n…® mati God…®n ensel…®n mam, egha n…® arazir kuraba ko arazir aghuibagh fo, manam dera, ez…® manam ikufi. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God n…® ko ik…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Atrivim oregha kamagh…®n amizim ikara, ‚ÄúA dera, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n azangs…®zir mam n…®n ti. K…® kamaghsua, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n guizbang…®ra na m…®k…®m…®va bizitam nan mongan mark…®.‚Äù
\p Ez…® amizim ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, atrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, n…® nan azang.‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúJoap ti akar kabav k…®masa n…® amadaz, o?‚Äù
\p Ez…® amizim ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, k…® n…®n ziam…®n guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, k…® n…®n azangs…®zim gitav…®raghan ibura, egh k…® uaghan akatam n…®n modoghan kogham. Are, bar guizbang…®ra, n…®n ingangarir gumazim Joap, an akar kabar na m…®kemegha, na amadaz…®ma k…® dar gun n…® m…®gei.
\v 20 N…®n ingangarir gumazim Joap, a pura dav kemezir puvat…®. An Apsalom…®n os…®mt…®zir kam ak…®rasa akar kabagh ami. Ez…® gumazir ekiam, n…® mati God…®n ensel…®n mam, n…® fofoziba ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuir av…®riba iti, egha n…® nguazir kam…®n otivir biziba bar dagh fo.‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® g…®n atrivim kamagh…®n Joap m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar dera, k…® n…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n mangam. Eght…® n…® mang…®va Apsalom inigh uamategh iz…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Joap kamagh…®n oregha Atrivim Devit…®n damazim…®n nguazim gir…®gha fuagha, uan guam nguazim m…®tuagha ziar ekiam a gan…®ga ghaze, ‚ÄúO atrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, God deraghv…®ra n…® damu. N…® nan azangs…®zim…®n g…®n ghuz…®, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, n…® na gifonge.‚Äù
\v 23 Egha Joap d…®kavigha Gesur…®n ghugha, Apsalom inigha uamategha Jerusalem…®n ize.
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúApsalom uan d…®penimra ik…®, egh a nan damazim…®n iz…® nan ganan mark…®.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Apsalom uan d…®penimra ikia egha atrivim…®n damazim…®n ghuzir puvat…®.
\s1 Devit Apsalom…®n arazir kuram g…®n amada
\p 
\v 25 Apsalom gumazir bar dirim, egha duar kuritam bar an namnam…®n dagarimning…®n ikegha uanaga an dapanir siriam…®n itir puvat…®. Israelian gumazitam an m…®n garir puvat…®, kamagh amiz…®, Israelia an ganasa bar akonge.
\v 26 An dapanir ar…®zim bar m…®temegha, aghua ruarvagha a baseir dughiam…®n, an azeniba vaghvagha gevir dughiam…®n an anep…®ri. Egha me dapanir ar…®zir a d…®p…®rizir kam…®n os…®mt…®zim…®n gari, an atrivim…®n skel…®n a kilogrem…®n pumuning…®n tu.
\v 27 Apsalom amuim…®n ikia otarir 3pla ikia egha guivir vam…®ra iti, an ziam Tamar. A bar amizir dirim.
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® Apsalom azenir pumuning…®n Jerusalem…®n ikia, egha tong bar atrivim…®n damazim…®n ghuzir puvat…®.
\v 29 Egha Apsalom Joap bagha akam amadagha ghaze, Joap Apsalom…®n amamangat…®ght…®, an atrivim bagh mang…®. Ez…® Joap Apsalom bagh mangan aghua. Ez…® a dughiar igharazim…®n uam Joap bagha akam amada, ez…® Joap ua mangan aghua.
\v 30 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Apsalom uan ingangarir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúJoap…®n balin azenim nan azenim…®n borogh…®n iti. Ia mang…®va a daboroght…®ma a isigh.‚Äù Ez…® me ghuava an balin azenim gaboroz…®ma a isi.
