\v 32 Ez…® Apsalom kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® iz…® uab…®n ganasa n…® bagha akaba amadima n…® izan aghua. K…® kamaghsua, n…® izegh nan akam inigh mang…®va atrivim…®n azaragh, a tizim bagha Gesur…®n na inigha Jerusalem…®n ize? K…® ti munagh…®ra ikia deraghai. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n atrivim…®n guam…®n ganasa, eght…® a nan arazir kuratam…®n apigh…®va, na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 33 Ez…® Joap ghugha Apsalom…®n akabar gun Atrivim Devit m…®gei. Atrivim oregha g…®vagha gumazir maba amadaz…®ma, me ghua Apsalom inigha izi. Ez…® Apsalom nguazim gir…®gha fuagha, uan guam nguazim m…®tuagha ziar ekiam atrivim gan…®ngi. Ez…® atrivim an tore.
\c 15
\s1 Apsalom Atrivim Devit batueghasa tuaviba buri
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® bizir kabar g…®n, Apsalom karis…®n mam ko, hoziar maba ko 50plan gumazir a geghuv an daroribar faragh mangamiba ini.
\v 2 A dughiaba vaghvagha bar m…®zarazibar, d…®kava ghua nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akam…®n zuir tuavir m…®riam…®n tuivav iti. Eght…® gumazir manam os…®mt…®zim ik…®va anek…®rs…® atrivim bagh iz…®t…®, Apsalom an diagh kamagh…®n an azaragham, ‚ÄúN…® nguibar manam…®n gumazim?‚Äù
\p Eght…® gumazir kam kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄúK…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, k…® Israel…®n anabar mam…®n gumazim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® Apsalom gumazir kam…®n os…®mt…®zim…®n m…®ngarim g…®fogha, kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh, n…®n akaba bar guizbang…®ra, egha dera. Ez…® noki, atrivim derav…®ra n…®n akaba baraghamin gumazitam am…®sevezir puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Egha Apsalom dughiabar zurara kamagh…®n gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúTav ti na m…®sevez…® k…® jas…®n otogha deraghai. Egh k…® gumazibar os…®mt…®ziba kot…®n da tuis…®gha deraghav…®ra da ak…®rai. K…® uab…® jas…®n otivasa ifonge.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Egh uaghan, gumazitam an ganigh a bagh iz…® ziar ekiam a dan…®ng…®s…® uan teviba ap…®rs…® damut…®, a zuam…®ra uan dafarimning an amadagh a muigh an toram.
\v 6 Gumazamizir uan os…®mt…®ziba inigha atrivim bagha zuiba, Apsalom arazir kamra me gami. An arazir kam…®n Israelian gumazamiziba, bar men n…®ghn…®zibagh etui.
\p 
\v 7 Azenir 4pla g…®vaz…®ma,\f + \fr 15:7 \ft Hibrun akam ghaze, 40plan azeniba. Ez…® fom…®ra gumazir maba akar kam Grigh…®n akam…®n a g…®ra, egha ghaze, akar kam a 4plan azenibav gei.\f* Apsalom ghua kamagh…®n Atrivim Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúGa uaning, n…® na teght…®ma k…® uamategh Hebron…®n mang…®, akar d…®k…®r…®zir k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamizir mam damight…®, an otoka.
\v 8 K…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, k…® Sirian kantrin aven itir nguibam Gesur…®n ikia, egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha akam ak…®ra ghaze, a ua na inigh Jerusalem…®n mang…®ght…®, k…® Hebron…®n nguibam…®n an ziam fam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® atrivim a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® navir am…®rizim sara mang…®.‚Äù Ez…® Apsalom uamategha Hebron…®n ghu.
\p 
\v 10 Apsalom uaghan Israelian anababa bar me m…®k…®masa modogha gumaziba amangi. Ez…® me kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa s…®ghar ararem baragh magh…®ra, kamagh…®n d…®m m…®k…®m, Apsalom Hebron…®n ikia atrivim…®n otogha g…®fa.‚Äù
\v 11 Apsalom Hebron…®n zuir dughiam…®n, a Jerusalem…®n 200plan gumazibar diaz…®, me a ko zui. Gumazir kaba, bizir a damuasava n…®ghn…®zim me a g…®fozir puvat…®, egha puram an g…®n zui.
\v 12 Me ghua Hebron…®n otivigha, Apsalom ofabagh ami. An ofan kabagh amir dughiam…®n, a Gilon gumazir mam Ahitofel, a inigh izasa gumazir maba amangiz…®, me Gilon nguibar ekiam…®n ghue. Ahitofel, a gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba isa Atrivim Devit gan…®dibar mav. A uan nguibam Gilo ategha Apsalom bagha ize. Dughiar kam…®n, Apsalom…®n n…®ghn…®zir kurar an averara amiba ek…®va zui. Ez…® an g…®n zuir gumazibar d…®bobonim ghuavanagav…®ra iti.
\s1 Devit Jerusalem ategha arav ghu
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® abuir gumazir mam iza kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n Israelian gumazamizibar navir averiaba, bar mogh…®ra Apsalom baghav…®ra iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n uan ingangarir gumazir dapanir Jerusalem…®n itibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAria, ia d…®kavigh e zuam…®ram Jerusalem ategh areka. Puvat…®ght…®, Apsalom e m…®sueght…® e bar ar…®ghiregham. E zuam…®ram areka, e suighsuight…®ma, Apsalom uan adarazi ko iz…® en nguibar ekiam gas…®ghas…®gh, en gumazamizibav sueght…® me ar…®ghiregham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazir dapaniba a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, atrivim en gumazir ekiam, n…® bizir tizim damuasa m…®gei, e a damuam.‚Äù
\v 16 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, atrivim uan d…®penim…®n itir darazi ko an ingangarir gumazir dapaniba, me d…®kavigha Jerusalem ategha uan suebar zui. Egha atrivim uan amuir dozir 10pla ataghiz…®, me atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n gara iti.
\p 
\v 17 Atrivim uan adarazi ko me Jerusalem ategha ghua, nguibar ekiam…®n itir d…®penir bar abuan dazighiam…®n itim…®n borogh…®n tuivighav iti.
\v 18 Egha atrivim tughav ikia garima, an ingangarir gumazir dapaniba ko a geghuva an faragha zuir m…®dorozir gumaziba, me a gitagha vorogh…®ra d…®ka arua zui, ez…® Keret ko, Peletian adarazi ko Get…®n nguibar ekiam…®n m…®dorozir gumazir 600pla, me uaghan a ko zui. Fom…®ra 600plan m…®dorozir gumazir kaba me Devit ko Get…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ike, me uaghan an g…®n ize.
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n Get…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapanim Itai m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha e ko mangasa? N…® kantrin igharazim…®n gumazim, n…® iza kagh iti, n…®n nguibam saghon iti. Kamagh…®n n…® uamategh Jerusalem…®n mang…®va Atrivim Apsalom ko ik…®.
\v 20 N…® dughiar otevimra kagh ike, kamagh…®n, k…® n…® damut…® n…® nguibar kam ategh pura e ko daruan kogham. E pura tintinibar ik…® daruam. Kamagh…®n, n…® uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigh uamategh mang…®t…® deragham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n apangkuvim ko an arazir a ia baghav…®ra itim, guizbang…®ra ia ko zurara ik…®.‚Äù\f + \fr 15:20 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Bar fom…®ra gumazir maba akar kam Grigh…®n akam…®n a giragha an osiri, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Aruam…®n akam Grigh…®n akam…®n g…®n zui.\f*
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Itai kamagh…®n Devit…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúO atrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam, ko n…®n ziam…®n, k…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, k…® zurara n…® ko ikiam. N…® nguibar manam…®n mang…®t…®, k…® uaghan an mangam. Egh me n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremegham, me uaghan na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúA dera, ia e ko mangam.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Itai uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko men amuiroghboriba ko, me faragha zuir darazir g…®n zui.
\v 23 Devit uan adarazi ko me Jerusalem atagh…®razir dughiam…®n, kantrin aven itir gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra puv…®ram azi. Ez…® atrivim uan adarazi ko me Kidron…®n Fanem giregha gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n amadaghan zui.
\p 
\v 24 Devit tughav ikia garima, gumazamiziba arua zuima, ofa gamir gumazimning Sadok ko Abiatar, ko Livaiba me uaghan me ko zui. Livaiba God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam gisaghpugha iza nguazim gat…®, egha uam a gisaghpuzir puvat…®gha, ikia ghuava dughiar gumazamiziba bar Jerusalem ataghizim…®n oto.
\v 25 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n Sadok m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam inigh uamategh nguibar ekiam…®n mang…®. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God na gifuegh, egh nan amamangat…®ght…® k…® ua iz…®, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam ko Purirpenir a itim…®n ganam.
\v 26 K…® pura iti. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God na gakueghan kogham, a dera, a bizir tizim…®n na damus…® a puram a damu.‚Äù
\p 
\v 27 Egha Devit ua kamagh…®n ofa gamir gumazim Sadok m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan akam deragha a g…®fos, o puvat…®? K…® kamagh…®n m…®gei. N…® uan otarim Ahimas ko Abiatar…®n otarim Jonatan, aning inigh ia uamategh navir am…®rizim sara nguibar ekiam…®n mang…®.
\v 28 N…® oragh, k…® mang…®va gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n otogh, fanem gira zuir danganim…®n borogh…®n ik…® ia m…®zuamam. Eght…® ia bizir Jerusalem…®n otiviziba dar akam na bagh anemadagh.‚Äù
\v 29 Ez…® Sadok ko Abiatar Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Boksiam inigha uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghugha iti.
\p 
\v 30 Ez…® Atrivim Devit bar osemegha uan dagarir asuamning suegha uan dapanim avaragha azia Oliv…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n ghuavanadi. Ez…® an g…®n zuir darasi, uaghan uan dapaniba avegha azia ghuavanadi.
\v 31 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n oraki, ‚ÄúAhitofel Apsalom ko an g…®n zuir darazir akurvaghasa ghu.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ga uaning, n…® Ahitofel…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh iraght…®, da bar pazav…®ram mang…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 Me ghua m…®ghs…®am…®n orazim…®n otifi, kar danganir me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fem. Ez…® Devit…®n namakar mam iza a bato, an ziam Husai, an Arkan ik…®zim…®n gumazim. An apangkuvir ekiam Devit…®n ikia uan korotiam abigha nguazim uan dapanim gaghui.
\v 33 Ez…® Devit an ganigha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® na ko iz…®t…®, k…® n…®n akurvaghs…® ingangarir ekiatam damigham.
\v 34 Egh n…® nan akurvaghs…®, n…® uamategh nguibar ekiam…®n mang…®, Apsalom…®n ganigh kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòO atrivim, k…® fom…®ra n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba n…®n afeziam gan…®ngi, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n otivasa.‚Äô N…® kamagh…®n damight…®, n…®ghn…®zir n…® Apsalom gan…®dir kam, a Ahitofel Apsalom gan…®ngizir n…®ghn…®zim atugham.
\v 35 N…® oragh. Ofa gamir gumazir pumuning, Sadok ko Abiatar, aning uaghan Jerusalem…®n iti. N…® atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n oraghizir biziba, bar adar gun aning m…®kemegh.
\v 36 Sadok…®n otarim Ahimas, ko Abiatar…®n otarim Jonatan, aning uaghan uan afeziamning ko iti. N…® oraghizir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba aning m…®kemeght…® aning iz…® na m…®k…®mam.‚Äù
\v 37 Ez…® Devit…®n namakam Husai, an akam…®n g…®n ghua uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghu. Husai ghua Jerusalem…®n otoz…®ma, Apsalom uaghan iza nguibar ekiam…®n oto.
\c 16
\s1 Siba tuavim…®n Devit bato
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 16:1 \xt 2 Samuel 9:9-10\x*Devit Husai ko m…®kemegha g…®vagha, a m…®ghs…®ar orazim ategha mong s…®vagha ghu. Ez…® Mefiboset…®n ingangarir gumazim Siba iza a bato. Siba 200plan bretba ko 100pla wain…®n ov…®zir me apuzizir ik…®ziba ko, 100plan temer fik…®n ov…®zibar ik…®ziba ko, memen inim…®n ingarizir m…®sevir wain…®n d…®pam ruiziba a da inigha izi. A dagher kaba isa donkin pumuning gis…®n da arigha Devit bagha izi.
\v 2 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n Siban azara, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha bizir kabar akua izi?‚Äù
\p Ez…® a kamagh…®n Devit ikara, ‚ÄúDonkin kamning, n…®n amuiba ko boriba aning daperagh mangam. Ez…® bretba ko temer figh…®n ov…®ziba, kar n…®n adarazi dar amam. Ez…® wain…®n kam, kar n…®n adarazi gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n daru mang…®t…®, m…®karziba men amiaght…®, me aneremam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 16:3 \xt 2 Samuel 19:26-27\x*Ez…® atrivim ghaze, ‚ÄúBar dera, n…® na m…®k…®m, n…®n gumazir ekiam Sol, an igiam Mefiboset managh iti?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Siba ghaze, ‚ÄúIsraelia ti dat…®r…®gh…®n anem…®seveght…®, a uan inazim Atrivim Sol…®n m…®n Israelia gativagh men ganam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Jerusalem…®n ikiav…®ra iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Atrivim Devit kamagh…®n oregha Siba m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Mefiboset…®n biziba bar n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Siba kamagh…®n Devit ikara, ‚ÄúAtrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, k…® n…®n damazim…®n tevimning ap…®righa ziar ekiam n…® gan…®di. K…® kamaghsua, bizir k…® damuamiba n…® damut…®, n…® na gifuegh…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\s1 Simei akar kurabar Devit m…®gei
\p 
\v 5 Atrivim Devit Siba ko m…®kemegha g…®vagha Bahurim…®n otogha g…®vagha garima, Sol…®n ik…®zim…®n mav, Geran otarim Simei, iza akar kurabav g…®a Devit…®n atara a bagha izi.
\v 6 Devit uan ingangarir gumazir dapaniba ko itima, Simei dag…®abar me ginifi. Devit uan m…®dorozir gumazir av…®ribar torim…®n arua zuima, Simei tong men atiatir puvat…®.
\v 7 Egha Simei Devit…®n atara ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® kamat…®gh. N…® gumazibav sozima da ariaghirir gumazim. N…® gumazir kuram, n…® kamat…®gh.
\v 8 N…® Sol batuegha an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. Egha n…® Sol…®n adarazir gumazir av…®ribav soghez…®ma, me ariaghire. Kamagh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…®n arazir kurar kam ikarvasi. Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…®n danganim iniasa, n…®n otarim Apsalom am…®sevez…®, a Israelian atrivim…®n oto. N…® gumazir gumazibav sozima me ariaghirim, kamagh…®n, God dat…®r…®k…®n n…® gas…®ghas…®si.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Seruian otarim Abisai kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, gumazir kam manmaghsua akar kurabav g…®a n…®n atari? An afiar aremezir kuam…®n m…®n gara iti. K…® ti mang…®va an f…®rim atugham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n Seruian otarimning Abisai ko Joap, aning m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKar guan bizim puvat…®. Anetakigh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God ti a m…®kemegha ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® akar kurabav k…®m Devit…®n atar,‚Äô eght…® a bizir kam bagh nan ataram, a dera. Eght…® tinara kamagh…®n an azaragham, ‚ÄòN…® tizim bagha Devit…®n atari?‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Egha Devit kamagh…®n Abisai ko uan ingangarir gumazir dapanir igharazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNan otarir nan otozimra na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeghasa, ez…® ia tizim bagha Benjamin…®n anabam…®n gumazir kam…®n adaribar d…®gavir kuram gami? Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®kemez…®ma, a bizir kam gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia aneteght…® an akar kabar amu.
\v 12 Ikiav…®ra Itir God nan arazir kurabar os…®mt…®zibagh fo, egh a ifongegh…®va, a ti adarir kurar dat…®r…®gh…®n otivizir kaba bagh arazir aghuim na ikaragh, deraghv…®ra na damuam.‚Äù
\v 13 Devit m…®kemegha g…®vagha, uan gumaziba ko tuavim…®n zui. Tuavir me zuir kamnang, a m…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n zuir tuavim. Ez…® Simei m…®ghs…®ar vuem…®n m…®riabar me gis…®n ghuava, Devit…®n atarava dag…®aba ko nguazir m…®nezibar a giniva zui.
\v 14 Ez…® atrivim uan gumazamiziba ko ghua danganir me zuim…®n otifi. Me bar amiagha danganir kam…®n avughsa iti.
\s1 Apsalom Jerusalem…®n oto
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® Apsalom ko Israelia bar ghua Jerusalem…®n otifi. Ez…® Ahitofel uaghan me ko ghu.
\v 16 Ez…® Devit…®n namakar aghuim Husai, a ghua Apsalom batogha an diagha kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® dughiar ruarim…®n atrivim…®n ik…®v…®ra ikiam!‚Äù
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® Apsalom akar kam baregha kamagh…®n Husai m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® Devit…®n namakar bar aghuim, manmagh…®n amiz…® n…® an g…®n ghuzir puvat…®? Kar namakar aghuibar arazir puvat…®. K…® n…®n ganigha d…®kavir kuram gami.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Husai kamagh…®n Apsalom m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko, gumazamizir kaba ko, Israelian igharaziba, me bar atrivitam am…®seveght…®ma, k…® an apengan ik…®va a ko ikiam.
\v 19 Egh k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n ikian kogh, egh k…® mang…® tinan ingangarir gumazim…®n ikiam? Puvat…®gham. K…® fom…®ra n…®n afeziam…®n ingangaribagh ami. Ez…® kamagh…®n, n…® an otarim, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®n ingangaribar amuam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® Apsalom kamagh…®n Ahitofel m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® dat…®r…®gh…®n na m…®k…®m, k…® bizir tizim damuam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Ahitofel ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® uan afeziam…®n amuir doziba ko daku, a me ataghiz…®ma me atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n gara iti. N…® kamagh…®n damight…®, Israelian gumazamiziba bar fogh suam, N…® guizbang…®ra uan afeziam gamiz…® a n…®n apanim…®n oto. Eght…® gumazamizir dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®n g…®n zuiba, me n…®n g…®n mang…®s…® bar gavgavigham.‚Äù
\v 22 \x - \xo 16:22 \xt 2 Samuel 12:11-12\x*Ahitofel kamagh…®n m…®kemez…®ma, me gumazir maba amadaz…®ma, me ghua atrivim…®n d…®penir siriam…®n avughsir danganim…®n, purirpenir mam…®n ingari. Egha gumazamiziba bar, men damazim…®n Apsalom an aven ghu. Ez…® me vaghvagha an afeziam…®n amuir doziba isa an aven zuima a me koma akui.
\p 
\v 23 Dughiar kam…®n gumazamiziba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Ahitofel me m…®geir akar kaba n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba me gan…®di. Ez…® da mati God uab…® me gan…®dir akaba, ez…® me guizbang…®ra dar g…®n zui. Devit faragha Ahitofel…®n akabar g…®n ghu, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Apsalom uaghan dar g…®n mangasa.
\c 17
\s1 Husai Apsalom gifara
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® g…®n Ahitofel kamagh…®n Apsalom m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® na amadaght…® k…® 12,000plan gumaziba inigh dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®mangan me ko, e Devit…®n g…®nt…®gham.
\v 2 A dat…®r…®gh…®n bar am…®ragha navim osemegha iti mogh…®ra, k…® mang…®va a ko m…®sogham. A d…®gavir kuram damight…®, an gumaziba ar…® mang…®t…® k…® atrivimra m…®sueght…® an aremegham.
\v 3 Egh k…® an gumazamiziba bar me inigh ua n…® bagh izam. Me mati amizim dat…®r…®gh…®ra pam…®n ikegha a basemegha arav ghugha, g…®n a uamategha uan pam bagha ize. N…® kamagh…®n ifonge, n…® Devit m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, gumazamiziba derav…®ra ikiam.‚Äù\f + \fr 17:3 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Bar fom…®ra gumazir maba akar kam Grigh…®n akam…®n a giragha an osiri, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Aruam…®n akam Grigh…®n akam…®n g…®n zui.\f*
\v 4 Apsalom ko Israelian gumazir dapaniba akar kam baregha kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, mar n…®ghn…®zir bar aghuimra.
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Apsalom ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Husain diaght…®, a iz…® uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n gun m…®k…®mt…® e a bareka.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Husai izez…®ma, Apsalom a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKar n…®ghn…®zir Ahitofel e gan…®ngizim, e an g…®n mangam o puvat…®gham? Puvat…®ght…®, n…® e m…®k…®m, e manmagh…®n damuam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Husai Apsalom…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…®ghn…®zir Ahitofel dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®ngizim, a derazir puvat…®.
\v 8 N…® fogh, n…®n afeziam Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, me m…®sozir gumazir gavgaviba, egha bar osemegha iti, me mati bean amebam gumazim an nguziba okemez…®ma, an navim isia iti. N…® uan afeziam…®n m…®dorozir arazibagh fo, a d…®mangan uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko dakuighan kogham.
\v 9 Egha a dat…®r…®gh…®n ti m…®ghs…®ar tam…®n dag…®ar torir ekiatam…®n modoghav ikiama, a danganir igharazitam…®n ikiama. Eght…® e dat…®r…®gh…®n mang…® me m…®soght…®ma, me en m…®dorozir gumazir tabav sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghireght…®, gumazamiziba akar kam baregh kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòApsalom…®n adarazi me bar ikufi.‚Äô
\v 10 Eght…® n…®n m…®dorozir gumazir igharaziba akar kam baregh bar atiatigham. Me uari mati m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba, egha laionbar m…®n tuifi. Ez…® Israelia bar fo, n…®n afeziam a m…®dorozibar faraghav…®ra zuir m…®dorozir gumazim, ez…® an m…®dorozir gumaziba bar puv…®ra m…®sosi.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúNan n…®ghn…®zim kamak…®n. N…® Israelian nguibabar itir gumazamiziba bar, not…®n amadaghan Dan…®n anabam…®n nguibam…®n ikegh, bar mang…® saut…®n amadaghan Berseban nguibam…®n otogh, dar gumazamiziba bar men diaght…®, me iz…® uari akuvagham. Me ongarir dadarim…®n gigim…®n m…®n bar av…®rasemegham. Eght…® n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n uab…® men faragh mang…®va ia Devit ko m…®sogh.
\v 12 Egh e Devit buri mang…® managh a batogh, e dat…®r…®gh…®n m…®zazim an adarazigh asam. Me bar en t…®vaghan kogham, mati d…®magarim…®n ghuariam irima, gumazitam anep…®ran iburagham. Eght…® Devit uan adarazi ko, e me m…®soght…®ma me bar ar…®m…®ghiregham. Eght…® men tav bar ikian kogham.
\v 13 Eght…® an ar…® nguibar ekiatam…®n aven mang…®ght…®ma, Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba benir gavgaviba inigh iz…® nguibar ekiar kam…®n d…®vaziba ikegh…®va, nguibar ekiar kam gekuigh danganir zarim…®n anekunight…®, a bar ikuvigham. Eght…® nguibar ekiar kam…®n dag…®ar muziaritam bar ikeghan kogham. Bar puvat…®gham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Husai m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, Apsalom ko Israelian gumaziba bar kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúHusain m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bar dera, egha Ahitofel…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh afira.‚Äù Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God faragha Apsalom gas…®ghas…®ghasa n…®ghn…®ki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uab…® men n…®ghn…®ziba fez…®, me Husain akabar g…®n zui. Guizbang…®ra Ahitofel…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba da dera, ez…® puvat…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me gamiz…®, me akar kam…®n g…®n ghuzir puvat…®.
\s1 Devit Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gha vong…®n ghu
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® bizir kam…®n g…®n, Husai ghua akar an Apsalom ko Israelian gumazir dapanibav m…®kemezibar gun ofa gamir gumazimning Sadok ko Abiatar m…®gei. Egha a uaghan Ahitofel…®n akabar gun aning m…®keme.
\p 
\v 16 Egha a ghaze, ‚ÄúGua zuam…®ra Devit bagh akam amadagh a m…®k…®m suam, Atrivim, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®mangan Jordan…®n Fanem vong…®n kagh dakuan mark…®, N…® fanem gir…®gh vong…®n mang…®. Puvat…®ght…®ma, Apsalom uan adarazi ko iz…®va, n…® ko n…®n adarazi sara bar ia m…®sueght…® ia ar…®m…®ghiregham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® Jonatan ko Ahimas, aning ghua Jerusalem…®n azenan Enrogel…®n Fanem…®n me m…®zua iti. Aning ofa gamir gumazimning…®n otarimning. Gumazamiziba aning…®n gant…® aning nguibar ekiam…®n aven mangan aghuagha, egha aning azenan modoghav iti. Ingangarir amizir mam faragha nguibar ekiar kam…®n otivir bizibar gun aning m…®gei. Ez…® aning ghua Devit m…®keme.
\v 18 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, gumazir igiar mam aning…®n ganigha ghua Apsalom m…®keme. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, aning zuam…®ra ghua Bahurim…®n nguibam…®n gumazir mam…®n d…®penim…®n ghu. Ez…® mozir d…®par mam an d…®penim borogh…®n iti, ez…® Jonatan ko Ahimas mozir kam giraghugha modo.
\v 19 Ez…® gumazir kam…®n amuim inir mam inigha iza an onegha mozir d…®par kam…®n akam avara. Egha a wit…®n maba inigha tintinibar inir kam gis…®n da ar…®ki. Eght…® gumaziba foghan kogham, aning kagh modoghav iti.
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® g…®n Apsalom…®n gumazir maba aning…®n g…®n iza kamagh…®n amizim…®n azai, ‚ÄúAhimas ko Jonatan managh iti?‚Äù
\p Ez…® amizim ghaze, ‚ÄúAning fanem gir…®gha vong…®n ghu.‚Äù Ez…® gumaziba ghua Ahimas ko Jonatan buriava aning…®n apizir puvat…®gha uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghu.
\p 
\v 21 Apsalom…®n gumaziba ghuegha g…®vaz…®, Ahimas ko Jonatan mozir kam ategha Atrivim Devit bagha ghugha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® kagh ikian mark…®. N…® uan adarazi bar me inigh zuam…®ra fanem gir…®gh vong…®n mang…®.‚Äù Egha aning g…®n Ahitofel Devit gas…®ghas…®ghasa m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bar a geghani.
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Devit akar kaba baregha g…®vagha, bem…®ra uan adarazi inigha Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gha vong…®n ghu. Ez…® am…®nim itima me vong…®n ghuegha g…®fa. Men tav ua danganir kam…®n itir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 23 \x - \xo 17:23 \xt 2 Samuel 15:12\x*Ahitofel garima Apsalom an akabar g…®n zuir puvat…®, ez…® a ghua uan donki gaperagha uamategha uan nguibar ekiam…®n ghu. A ghua uan biziba ko amuim ko boriba ak…®righa g…®n ghua uab…® aguraghava areme. Ez…® an amuim ko boriba an kuam inigha ghua, an afeziabar kuaba afezir danganim…®n anefa.
\p 
\v 24 Egha Apsalom ko Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba d…®kavigha Devit…®n g…®n zui. Ez…® dughiar Apsalom ghua Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gha vong…®n zuim…®n, Devit uan adarazi ko ghua Mahanaim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otogha g…®fa.
\v 25 Apsalom faragha Amasa am…®sevez…®ma, a Joap…®n danganim inigha an m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapanim…®n iti. Amasa Jeter…®n otarim, a Ismael…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazir mam,\f + \fr 17:25 \ft Hibrun akam ziar kam Ismael itir puvat…®. A ghaze, Israel. Ez…® fom…®ra gumazir maba akar kam Grigh…®n akam a giragha an osiri, egha me ghaze, a Ismael m…®gei. 1 Eghaghaniba 2:17, uaghan Ismael m…®gei.\f* egha a Nahas…®n guivim Abigel…®n iti. Ez…® Joap…®n amebam Seruia, an Abigel…®n amezemebam.
\v 26 Dughiar kam…®n, Apsalom Israelia ko ghua Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n otivigha averpenibar ingari.
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® Devit ghua Mahanaim…®n otozir dughiam…®n, gumazir 3pla iza a bato. Men ziabar kara, Sobi a Nahas…®n otarim, a kantri Amon…®n nguibar ekiam Raban gumazim. Ez…® Amiel…®n otarim Makir, a Lodebar…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazim. Ez…® Barsilai, a Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n Rogelim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazim.
\v 28-29 Gumazir kaba itariba ko nguazir m…®neba, ko daguraguir m…®siaba is…® Devit uan gumaziba ko me dan…®ngasa da inigha zui. Egha me dagher maba sara inigha zui, kar wit ko bali, plaua ko wit…®n me avim…®n tueziba, ko nguezir igharagha garir pumuning ko, hani ko, bulmakaun otem ko dagher sis…®n me bulmakaun oter eborim…®n ingarizim. Me uaghan sipsip…®n maba inigha ghue. Me kamagh…®n fo, Devit uan gumaziba ko iza gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n zuir tuavim…®n ize. Ez…® m…®tiriam men azima kuariba men p…®ri, ez…® men m…®karziba bar men amia. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me dagher kaba inigha me bagha izi, eght…® me dar am…®va ua gavgavim iniam.
\c 18
\s1 Joap Apsalom m…®soghez…®ma, an areme
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Atrivim Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me akuvagha, dar 1,000plan m…®dorozir gumazir okoruaba vaghvagha me bagha faragha zuir gumazir dapaniba am…®sevegha, egha uaghan kamagh…®ra 100plan m…®dorozir gumaziba bagha gumazir dapanir maba am…®sefe.
\v 2 Egha uan m…®dorozir gumaziba 3plan okoruabar me ab…®ki. Joap okoruar mam gativagha an garima, an aveghbuam Abisai mam…®n garima, Get…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazim Itai okoruar mam…®n gari. Egha Devit kamagh…®n uan m…®dorozir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® uab…® ia ko e m…®soghs…® mangam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. N…® e ko mangan kogham. E bar m…®dorozim…®n areght…®, me e g…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. Egh me en taraziv sueght…®, e ar…®m…®ghireght…®, me uaghan gumazir aremezibagh n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. Ez…® n…® e ko mang…®t…®, me n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeght…®, bizir kam mati me 10,000plan gumazibav soghez…® me bar ariaghire. E ghaze, kamagh…®n ti deragham, n…® nguibar ekiam…®n kagh…®ra ik…®. Eght…® e gumaziba o bizitabar oteveght…®, n…® e bagh da amangam.‚Äù
\v 4 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, k…® ian n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n mangam.‚Äù Egha Devit d…®vazir nguibar ekiam av…®nizim…®n tiar akar ekiam…®n m…®riam…®n tughav ikia garima, m…®dorozir gumazibar sueba vorogh…®ra d…®ka azenan zui. M…®dorozir gumaziba vaghvagha uan okoruabar aven iti, okoruar mam…®n d…®bobonim 1,000plan gumaziba iti, ez…® okoruar mam…®n d…®bobonim 100plan gumaziba iti. Egha me bar uan okoruabar vorogh…®ra d…®ka aven zui.
\p 
\v 5 Devit akar gavgavim…®n Joap ko Abisai ko Itai m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa na bagh n…®ghnigh, gumazir igiar kam Apsalom…®n apangkufigh.‚Äù Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba bar, akar gavgavir Devit uan m…®dorozir gumazir dapanibagh an…®ngiziba, me bar da baraki.
\p 
\v 6 Egha Devit…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ghua Israelia bato, kar Apsalom…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba. Egha me Efraim…®n anabam…®n ruarim…®n uariv sosi.
\v 7-8 Me uariv sogha ghua, Devit…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba bar Israelia ab…®nigha bar me gas…®ghas…®ki. M…®dorozim bar ekevegha bar distrigh…®n danganiba bar a da ini. Gumazir bar av…®rim ruarim…®n aven tintinibar onganigha ariaghire. Kamagh amiz…® ruarim…®n aven ariaghirezibar d…®bobonim, a m…®dorozim…®n ariaghirezir darazir d…®bobonim gafira. M…®dorozir gumazir dughiar kamran ariaghireziba bar dar d…®bobonim, 20,000…®n tu.
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Apsalom donki gaperagha ghua, Devit…®n m…®dorozir gumazir maba batogha ara zui, ez…® an donki ok…®n temer ekiar mam…®n apengan zuima, an dapanir ar…®zim temer aguar mam…®n guragha gavgafi. Ez…® Apsalom guraghav itima, an donki ivemara ghuav…®ra iti, ez…® Apsalom overiam ko nguazim…®n t…®zim…®n guraghav iti.
\v 10 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir kabar mav, Apsalom…®n ganigha ghua Joap m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Apsalom…®n garima, a temer ok…®n aguam…®n guraghav iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Joap a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúBizir kam ti guizbang…®ra, o? Ez…® n…® a m…®sueght…® an aremeghan aghua? N…® a m…®soghez…® an aremez…®, k…® ti 10plan silvan dag…®aba, ko m…®dorozir gumazibar let…®n tam n…® ganighai.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® gumazir kam kamagh…®n Joap ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® silvan dag…®ar 1,000pla is…® na dan…®ngight…®, k…® bizitam…®n atrivim…®n otarim damighan kogham. E bar ikiava orazima, atrivim akar gavgavir kam isa n…® ko Abisai ko Itai, a ia m…®keme. A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa gumazir igiar kam Apsalom…®n ganigh…®va, a gas…®ghas…®ghan mark…®.‚Äô
\v 13 K…® atrivim…®n akam batuegha Apsalom m…®soghez…® an aremeghai, kamagh…®n atrivim bizir k…® amizir kam bareghai. Guizbang…®ra, atrivim zurara bizir otivibar akaba, a bar da barasi. Ez…® k…® amizir bizir kam, atrivim a baregh, kamagh…®n a na is…® kotiam dat…®ght…®, k…® fo, n…® kotiam…®n aven nan akuraghan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Joap a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúMark…®, k…® n…® ko m…®k…®man aghua.‚Äù Egha Joap ghua afuzir 3pla inigha temer Apsalom guraghav itir kam bagha ghu. Ez…® Apsalom angam…®ra itima, Joap afuzibar an d…®ghorim ginifi.
\v 15 Ez…® Apsalom aremeghasava amima, 10plan m…®dorozir gumazir Joap…®n afuziba ko biziba ateriba, ivegha Apsalom…®n borogh…®n iza bar an kuam am…®ghiz…®, an areme.
\p 
\v 16 Apsalom aremegha g…®vaz…®ma, Joap m…®dorozim ag…®vasa m…®dorozir gumazir mam m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® s…®gham givit…®ma, Devit…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba oregh…®va m…®dorozim atakigh. Ez…® Devit…®n adarazi s…®gham baregha Israelian ag…®nt…®zir arazim ategha uamategha ize.
\v 17 Egha me ruarim…®n ghua Apsalom…®n kuam inigha mozir konir mam…®n anekuniz…®, a iraghu. Egha dag…®ar av…®riba isa an mozim m…®k…®rav itima, dag…®ar pozir bar ekiam anagava oto. Ez…® Israelia uamategha ara uan nguibaba vaghvagha dar ghue.
\p 
\v 18 Apsalom fom…®ra angam…®ra itir dughiam…®n, a dag…®ar ruarir ekiar mam inigha Atrivim…®n Danganir Zarim…®n uan ziam…®n ababanim gamuava, anesara. Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® otarir nan danganim iniamba puvat…®, eght…® a Israelia damut…®, me na g…®n…®ghn…®gham.‚Äù A bizir kam bagha uan ziam isa dag…®ar kam gat…®. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazamiziba uaghan dag…®ar kam d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúApsalom…®n Dag…®am.‚Äù\f + \fr 18:18 \ft Akar kam, ‚Äúdat…®r…®gh…®n,‚Äù an en dughiar kam m…®geir puvat…®. A dughiar gumazir ak…®nafarir kam osirizim m…®gei.\f*
\s1 Me Apsalom…®n ovevem…®n gun Devit geghani
\p 
\v 19 Apsalom aremegha g…®vaz…®ma, Sadok…®n otarim Ahimas kamagh…®n Joap m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa na ateght…® k…® atrivim bagh ivegh mang…®va eghaghanir aghuir Ikiav…®ra Itir God an apanibar gavgavim ab…®razim…®n a geghanam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® Joap a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®, n…® dat…®r…®k…®n atrivim bagh eghaghanir aghuim inigh mangan kogham. An otarim aremegha g…®fa, kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® dughiar igharazitam…®n mang…®t…® deragham.‚Äù
\v 21 Dughiar kam, Itiopian gumazir mam iti, an atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazim. Ez…® Joap a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…®va, bizir n…® ganizibar gun atrivim geghan.‚Äù Ez…® a Joap…®n damazim…®n uan tevimning ap…®righa, d…®kavigha Devit bagha ivemara zui.
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Sadok…®n otarim Ahimas ua Joap gaghora ghaze, ‚ÄúBizir tizir na bativamiba, k…® dagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. K…® kamaghsua, n…® na ateght…® k…® uaghan Itiopian gumazir kam…®n g…®n mang…®va atrivim geghanasa.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Joap kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄúNan otarim, n…® bizir tizim bagh mangasa? N…® mang…® a m…®kemegh an bizir aghuitam inighan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® Ahimas ghaze, ‚ÄúBizir tizim na bativam, k…® mangam.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Joap ghaze, ‚ÄúAria n…® mang…®.‚Äù Ez…® Ahimas ivegha Jordan…®n Fanem mogh…®n ghua, Itiopian gumazir kam gitagha faragha ghu.
\p 
\v 24 Dughiar kam…®n, Devit nguibar ekiam…®n aven itir d…®vazim…®n tiar akam ko azenan itir d…®vazim…®n tiar akamning…®n t…®zim gaperaghav iti. Nguibar ekiam geghuva an garir gumazir mam ghua, tiar akam…®n borogh…®n d…®vazir gavgavim gis…®n tughav ikia garima, gumazir vam…®ra ivegha izi.
\v 25 Ez…® gumazir kam iza atrivim…®n diagha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir mam ivemara izi.‚Äù
\p Ez…® atrivim ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir vam…®ra ivemar iz…®t…®, e suam mar gumazir eghaghanir aghuim inigha izim.‚Äù Ez…® gumazim ivemara rogh…®ra izi.
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® nguibar ekiam geghuva an garir gumazim ua gari, gumazir igharazir mam uaghan ivegha izi. Ez…® a gumazir tiar akam…®n gara itim…®n diagha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® gan gumazir igharazir mam uaghan ivemara izi.‚Äù
\p Ez…® atrivim ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir igharazir mam uaghan eghaghanir aghuitam inigha izi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® eghuvir gumazim ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® garima, faragha ivegha izir gumazim, mati Sadok…®n otarim Ahimas ivemari.‚Äù
\p Ez…® atrivim ghaze, ‚ÄúA gumazir aghuim. A ti eghaghanir aghuitam sara izama.‚Äù
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® Ahimas rogh…®ra iza kamagh…®n atrivim…®n diagha ghaze, ‚ÄúE deraghav…®ra iti.‚Äù
\p Egha an atrivim…®n borogh…®n izava, nguazim gir…®gha fuagha, uan guam nguazim m…®tuagha ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim, n…® nan ekiam, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fam, a n…®n God. Gumazir n…® batogha n…® ko m…®soziba, a me isa en dafarim gat…®z…® e me ab…®ni.‚Äù
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n Ahimas…®n azara, ‚ÄúNan borim Apsalom deragha iti, o puvat…®?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Ahimas kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim, Joap d…®kavigha, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, ko n…®n Itiopian ingangarir gumazim amadir dughiam…®n, k…® garima, gumazir av…®rim pamtem…®n diav arai. Ez…® k…® derav…®ra fozir puvat…®, me bizir tizim gami.‚Äù
\p 
\v 30 Ez…® atrivim a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® s…®vagh mang…® magh tugh.‚Äù Ez…® a is…®vagha ghua munagh tughav iti.
\p 
\v 31 Ez…® Itiopian gumazir kam iza kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim, n…® nan gumazir ekiam, k…® eghaghanir aghuim n…® dan…®ngasa izi. Gumazir n…® ko m…®soghava n…® batoziba, dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…®n akuraz…®, me uam arazir kuratam…®n n…® damuan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 Ez…® atrivim oregha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan borim Apsalom, a deraghav…®ra iti o puvat…®?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Itiopian gumazim kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim, k…® kamagh…®n ifonge, arazir dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazir igiar kam batozim, a gumazir n…®n apanim gamua n…® ko m…®soziba bar me batifigh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 33 Ez…® atrivim akar kam baregha an navim bar a baseme, ez…® a d…®kavigha nguibam…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n itir d…®penim…®n ghuriar p…®n itim…®n ghuanabogha azi. An aven ghugha kamagh…®n azia m…®gei, ‚ÄúO nan otarim Apsalom, nan otarim, nan otarim Apsalom. K…® n…®n danganim inigha aremez…® ti deraghai. O Apsalom, nan otarim, nan otarim!‚Äù
\c 19
\s1 Joap akar gavgavim Devit gan…®ngi
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® gumazir maba g…®n ghua kamagh…®n Joap…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúDevit bar Apsalom…®n apangkuvigha a bagha azia iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 2 Dughiar kam…®n Devit…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba kamagh…®n oraki, Devit uan otarim Apsalom bagh azia iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me m…®dorozim damu apaniba ab…®namin arazim bagha navir agorogem gamir puvat…®. Men naviba osemegha iti.
\v 3 Egha m…®dorozir gumaziba n…®m…®ra n…®m…®ra nguibar ekiam…®n iza, mati m…®dorozir gumaziba m…®dorozim…®n aregha aghums…®zim sara izi.
\v 4 Dughiar kam…®n, atrivim uan guam avaragha pamtem…®n azia ghaze, ‚ÄúO Apsalom, nan otarim, noka. Apsalom, nan otarim, nan otarim!‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Joap atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n ghugha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh. N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n uan m…®dorozir gumazibagh amiz…®, me bar aghums…®ki. Dughiar kamra, gumazir kaba n…®n akura. Ez…® n…® uan amuiba ko boriba ko amuir doziba, ia os…®mt…®zir tam inizir puvat…®.
\v 6 Ez…® gumazir n…® gifongeziba, n…® me gifongezir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazir n…® gifongezir puvat…®ziba n…® me gifonge. N…®n arazim bighav…®ra kamagh…®n en akagha ghaze, n…®n ingangarir gumazir dapaniba ko m…®dorozir gumaziba, me pura biziba. Ez…® k…® fo, Apsalom ti angam…®ra itima e bar ariaghirez…®, n…® ti bar akongeghai.
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúN…® oragh, n…® d…®kavigh zuam…®ra mang…® m…®dorozir gumaziba derav…®ra me m…®k…®m…®va, men navibar amight…® da deraka. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, n…® kamagh…®n damighan koght…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®mangan me n…® ateght…®, n…® bar os…®mt…®zir ekiam iniam. Eght…® os…®mt…®zir kam os…®mt…®zir n…® uan igiamra ikia iza dat…®r…®gh…®n tuzir os…®mt…®ziba, bar dagh afiragham.‚Äù
\v 8 Joap m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, Devit d…®kavigha ghua nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akam…®n aperaghav iti. Ez…® an m…®dorozir gumaziba kamagh…®n oraki, atrivim nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n aperaghav iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an m…®dorozir gumaziba iza a ko iti. Ez…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba arava vaghvagha bar uan nguibabar ghue.
\s1 Judaba ua Jerusalem…®n ikiasa, Devit…®n azangs…®si
\p 
\v 9 Israelian gumazamiziba bar, uari adoghodogha marazi ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim Devit en akuraz…®ma, Filistiaba ko apanir igharaziba e gas…®ghas…®zir puvat…®. Egha a dat…®r…®gh…®n, Apsalom…®n atiatigha arav ghugha en kantri ataki.
\v 10 E Apsalom am…®sevez…® a en atrivim…®n otoz…®, me m…®dorozim…®n aven a m…®soghez…® an areme. E Devit inigh iz…®t…® a en atrivim…®n ikiam. E bizir tizim m…®zuamam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Gumazir maba Israelian m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n gun Atrivim Devit geghani, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a ofa gamir gumazimning, Sadok ko Abiatar bagha akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® kamagh…®n ifonge, ia nan akam is…® Judabar gumazir dapanibav m…®k…®m suam, k…® kagh ikia Israelia m…®geir akaba baraki. Ia Judaba bizir tizim bagha Israelia ataghiz…®, me faraghav…®ra nan azangs…®gha ghaze, k…® ua uan d…®penim…®n mangam?
\v 12 E bar aveghbuaba egha anabar vam…®rara, egha ia tizim bagha gumazir igharaziba ataghiz…® me ian faragh mang…®, uam na inigh izasa?‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Egha Devit uaghan Amasa m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGa anabar vam…®ra. K…® n…® am…®seveght…®ma, n…® Joap…®n danganim inigh, nan m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapanim…®n ikiam. K…® kamagh…®n damighan koght…® God na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Devit…®n akaba, Judan gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®zibagh ekuiz…®, me n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ram amigha kamagh…®n a bagha akam amadagha ghaze, ‚ÄúE ifonge, n…® uan adarazi ko, ia bar uamategh Jerusalem…®n iz…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Devit uan adarazi ko ghua Jordan…®n Fanem…®n otifi. Ez…® Judan gumazamiziba kamaghsua, Devit iz…® Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®ght…®, me a bativigh a ko Jordan…®n vong…®n izam. Egha me ghua Jordan…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®n, Gilgal…®n nguibar ekiam…®n a m…®zuai iti.
\v 16 \x - \xo 19:16 \xt 2 Samuel 16:5-13\x*Ez…® Geran otarim Simei, a Benjamin…®n anabam…®n mav, an nguibam Bahurim, a zuam…®ra Judaba ko iza Atrivim Devit bativasa izaghir…®.
\v 17 Ez…® Benjamin…®n anabam…®n 1,000plan gumaziba Simei ko Devit bagha ize. Ez…® Siba, a Sol…®n adarazir ingangarir gumazim, a 15plan otariba ko 20plan ingangarir gumaziba sara, zuam…®ra ghua Jordan…®n Fanem…®n atrivim bato.
\v 18 Me atrivim…®n adarazir akurvagha, me isa fanem…®n vong…®n me ar…®si.\f + \fr 19:18 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* Egha atrivim ifongezir biziba, me bar dagh ami.
\s1 Devit Simein apangkufi
\p 
\v 19 Atrivim d…®pam g…®rasava amima, Simei iza an damazim…®n ir…®gha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGa uaning, nan gumazir ekiam, n…® nan arazir kuraba g…®n amangasa k…® ifonge. N…® Jerusalem ataghizir dughiam…®n, os…®mt…®zir k…® amizim, n…® a g…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, n…® nan arazir kurar kam bar a g…®n amadagh.
\v 20 Atrivim, k…® fo, k…® arazir kuram gami, kamagh…®n amiz…® k…® not…®n amadaghan gumazir igharazibar faragha iza n…® bato. K…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Seruian otarim Abisai kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúSimei akar kuram…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®sevezir atrivim m…®keme, kamagh…®n an aremeght…®, deragham!‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n Abisai uan avebam Joap ko aning m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKar guan bizim puvat…®, gua Seruian otarimning. Gua tizim bagha nan apanim damuasa? K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n kamagh…®n fo, k…® Israelia bar men atrivim. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, e Israelian gumazitam m…®sueght…® an aremeghan kogham. Bar puvat…®gham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 23 Egha atrivim akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamua pamtem…®n Simei m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, me n…® m…®sueght…®, n…® aremeghan kogham.‚Äù
\s1 Devit Mefiboset…®n apangkufi
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 19:24 \xt 2 Samuel 9:1-13; 16:1-4\x*Ez…® Sol…®n igiavotarim Mefiboset uaghan iza Devit bato. Dughiar Devit Jerusalem ataghizim…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, atrivim uamategha deragha izezim…®n, Mefiboset uan dagariba ko korotiaba ruezir puvat…®, egha a uaghan uan ghuamas…®zim g…®sezir puvat…®.
\v 25 Mefiboset dat…®r…®gh…®n Jerusalem ategha\f + \fr 19:25 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* iza atrivim bato. Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúMefiboset, n…® manmagh…®n amigha na ko arav ghuzir puvat…®?‚Äù
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® Mefiboset kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúO atrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, n…® fo, nan dagarimning ikufi. Dughiar n…® Jerusalem atagh…®razim…®n, k…® uan ingangarir gumazim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® na bagh donkin tam inigh iz…®t…®, k…® a daperagh atrivim ko mangam.‚Äô Ez…® nan ingangarir gumazim na gifara.
\v 27 Egha a n…® bagha ghua akar ifavaribar n…® m…®g…®a nan ziam ab…®ra. Ez…® atrivim, n…® nan gumazir ekiam, n…® mati Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel. N…® bizir aghuir manam…®n na damus…® n…® a damu.
\v 28 K…® fo, n…® nan afeziam…®n adarazir gumazamiziba bar me m…®sueght…® me arighireghamin gavgavim iti. Ez…® puvat…®, n…® nan apangkuvigha na ataghiz…®, k…® zurara n…®n d…®penim…®n aven itir dagher dakozim…®n api. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ua bizir igharaz tam uab…® dan…®ng…®s…® n…®n azangan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam mamagh…®ra tugh, k…® n…®ghnigha g…®fa. N…® Siba ko gua Sol…®n nguazim tuiragh uaning dan…®ng, an akuar tam init…®ma n…® akuatam inigh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 30 Ez…® Mefiboset kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Siba ateght…®, a bar ada ini. K…® dagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. K…® n…® baghav…®ra n…®ghn…®zima, n…® deraghav…®ra ikegha ua ize.‚Äù
\p 
\v 31 \x - \xo 19:31 \xt 2 Samuel 17:27-29\x*Ez…® Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n gumazim Barsilai, a Rogelim…®n nguibam ategha izaghira atrivim ko Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gh vong…®n mangasa a ko iti.
\v 32 Barsilai dat…®r…®gh…®n 80plan azeniba ikia egha bar ghuri. A dag…®ar av…®riba iti, ez…® Devit uan adarazi ko Mahanaim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Barsilai dagheba ko bizir av…®ribar Devit uan adarazi ko me gan…®di.
\v 33 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan g…®n Jerusalem…®n iz…®t…® k…® n…® geghuv n…®n ganam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 34 Ez…® Barsilai a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúNan gumazir ekiam, k…® k…®ran oveghang…®n aremegham, ez…® k…® tizim bagh n…®n g…®n Jerusalem…®n mangam?
\v 35 N…® oragh, k…® 80plan azeniba iti, egha deragha bizir aghuiba ko kurabagh fozir puvat…®. K…® dagheba ko d…®pabar am…®va deragh dar is…®ngt…®ziba baraghan kogham, manam deraz…® manam ikufi. Nan kuarimning uaghan ikufi, eght…® gumazamiziba ighiabar amut…®, k…® me onger ighiaba baraghan kogham. Kamagh amiz…®, k…® tizim bagh n…®n g…®n mang…®va os…®mt…®zim n…® dan…®ngam? Ti puvat…®gham.
\v 36 Atrivim, n…® bizir tizim bagh arazir aghuir kam…®n na damuasa? Mark…®. K…® n…® ko fanem…®n vong…®n tong s…®vagh mang…®gh, egh k…® uamategham.
\v 37 Ga uaning, n…® na ateght…® k…® uamategh uan nguibam…®n mang…®va, nguazir uan afeziam ko amebam…®n kuamning afaz…® nagh…®n aremeka. Ez…® nan otarim Kimham iti, a n…® ko mangam. A n…®n ingangarir gumazim. Eght…® n…® bizitam a bagh a damus…® n…® puram a damu.‚Äù
\p 
\v 38 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúKimham na ko mangam. Ez…® k…® bizir tizim a bagh a damus…® ifongegh, k…® puram a damuam. Egh n…® bizir tizim damus…® pura nan azaraght…®, k…® n…® bagh puram a damuam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 39 Egha atrivim uan gumazamiziba ko, me bar Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gha vong…®n ghue. Egha atrivim deragh Barsilai damuasa God ko m…®gei. Egha a Barsilain torez…®, a uamategha uan nguibam…®n ghu.
\v 40 Atrivim vong…®n ghua Gilgal…®n nguibar ekiam…®n zuima, Kimham a ko zui. Ez…® Judabar m…®dorozir gumaziba ko Israelian marasi, me bar atrivim ko vong…®n zui.
\s1 Israelia ko Judaba uari adoghodosi
\p 
\v 41 Devit Gilgal…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itima, Israelian gumaziba bar atrivim bagha iza, kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, bizir tizim bagha en aveghbuaba Judaba, en modogha n…® ko n…®n amuiba ko boriba ko n…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha Jordan…®n Fanem ab…®ki?‚Äù
\p 
\v 42 Judan gumaziba bar akar kam baregha kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim en ik…®zim…®n mav, kamagh…®n amiz…® e arazir kam gami. Ez…® ia tizim bagha e baseme? Atrivim e bagha daghetam givezezir puvat…®, egha bizitam bar e gan…®ngizir puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 43 Ez…® Israelian gumaziba kamagh…®n me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazitam atrivim…®n otogh…®va a bar mogh…®ra en kantrin atrivim…®n ikiam. Ez…® kantrin kam…®n aven, e Israelia 10plan anababa iti, ez…® ia Judaba anabar vam…®rara iti. Guizbang…®ra, Devit ian anabam…®n oto, egha a bar en atrivim…®n iti, ez…® e 10plan anababa, e ia gafira. Ez…® ia tizim bagha en aghuagha e gas…®ghas…®ghasava ami? E uari uam atrivim inigh izamin n…®ghn…®zim…®n m…®ngarim.‚Äù Ez…® puvat…®, Judaba bar gavgavigha pamtem…®n m…®g…®a Israelia ab…®ni.
\c 20
\s1 Seba atrivim ab…®nasa
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 20:1 \xt 1 Atriviba 12:16; 2 Eghaghaniba 10:16\x*Dughiar kam…®n gumazir kurar mam iti, an ziam Seba. A Bikrin otarim, a Benjamin…®n anabam…®n gumazir mam. Egha Seba s…®gham givia d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúDevit mark…®, e an anabam…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®. E Jesin otarim…®n adarazi puvat…®, e an g…®n mangan kogham. Aria, e Israelian gumazamiziba uamategh uan nguibabar mangam.‚Äù
\v 2 Ez…® Israelia akar kam baregha, bar Devit ategha Seba ko zui. Ez…® Judan gumaziba Devit…®n g…®n ghua, Jordan…®n Fanem ategha tuavim…®n ghua Jerusalem…®n otifi.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 20:3 \xt 2 Samuel 16:22\x*Me ghua Jerusalem…®n otivigha g…®vagha, Devit uan atrivir d…®penim…®n aven ghugha, uan 10plan amuir dozir an atrivir d…®penim…®n ganasa taghiziba, a me inigha d…®penir igharazim…®n me arigha, men ganasa gumazir maba m…®sefe. Egha marazi am…®sevez…®ma, me dagheba ko bizir igharaziba sara me gan…®di. Egha a fom…®ra me gami mogh…®n, a ua ghua me ko akuir puvat…®. Me zurara pura d…®penim…®n iti, mati amizir odiariba.
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® atrivim g…®n kamagh…®n Amasa m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® Judan gumazibar diagh me akufagh. Egh gurum m…®zaraghan o zuerim…®n ia bar iz…® na batogh. Egh n…® uaghan me ko ik…®.‚Äù
\v 5 Ez…® Amasa men d…®masa ghua, egha a zuam…®ra men diazir puvat…®, ez…® atrivim me izasa d…®borozir dughiam, a g…®vaz…® me t…®ghar izam.
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n Abisai m…®gei, ‚ÄúApsalom os…®mt…®zir ekiam e gan…®ngi, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Bikrin otarim Seba, os…®mt…®zir bar ekiam e dan…®ngam, eght…® Seban os…®mt…®zim bar ekevegh Apsalom…®n os…®mt…®zim gafiragham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® nan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigh mang…® an ag…®ragh an suiragh. Puvat…®ght…® Seba uan adarazi ko mang…® nguibar ekiar d…®vazir gavgaviba itibar ik…®t…®, e an suighan iburagham.‚Äù\f + \fr 20:6 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Abisai, ko Joap…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba, ko atrivim geghuvir m…®dorozir gumaziba, kar Keretia ko Peletian m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba, me bar Jerusalem ategha, Bikrin otarim Seban ag…®nt…®ghasa ghue.
\v 8 Me ghua Gibeon…®n dag…®ar ekiam…®n otoz…®, Amasa iza me bato. Dughiar kam…®n, Joap m…®dorozir korotiam arugha m…®dorozir sabam inigha uan letiam…®n anem…®gh…®r…®. M…®dorozir sabar kam uan m…®sevim…®n aven iti, ez…® Joap Amasan borogh…®n zuir dughiam…®n m…®dorozir sabam suiagh…®r…®gha nguazim gir…®.
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Joap kamagh…®n Amasa m…®gei, ‚ÄúAruer ar…®zim aveghbuam, n…® deraz, o?‚Äù Egha uan agharir guvim…®n an ghuamas…®zim…®n suiragha, an torasa.
\v 10 Joap m…®dorozir sabar mam uan agharir k…®riam…®n an suira, ez…® Amasa m…®dorozir sabar kam…®n ganizir puvat…®. Joap Amasan navim b…®raz…®ma, an muriam suiagh…®r…®gha nguazim gir…®z…®, a magh…®ram areme. Ez…® Joap uam a b…®razir puvat…®. Joap Amasa b…®raz…® an aremez…®, a uan aveghbuam Abisai ko aning Bikrin otarim Seban ag…®nt…®ghasa ghu.
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Joap…®n m…®dorozir gumazir mam Amasan kuam…®n borogh…®n tughav ikia d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir Devit ko Joap gifongeziba, me Joap…®n g…®n mang…®.‚Äù
\v 12 Ez…® ghuzim bar Amasan kuam noghez…®, an kuam tuavir torim gir…®ghav iti. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba bar iza an kuam…®n ganigha ua zuir puvat…®. Ez…® Joap…®n m…®dorozir gumazir kam gari me zuir puvat…®z…®ma, a an kuam gekuigha ghua tuavim ategha tuzir torim…®n anet…®gha inim…®n anevara.
\v 13 Ez…® Amasan kuam ua tuavim…®n itir puvat…®z…®ma, m…®dorozir gumaziba bar Joap…®n g…®n ghua Seba buri.
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Seba ghua Israelian anababa bar men nguaziba abigha ghua, nguibar ekiam Abel Betmakan oto. Ez…® Berin ik…®zim…®n gumaziba bar, a ko uari akuvagha a ko ghua nguibar ekiam…®n aven ghue.
\v 15 Ez…® Joap…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba kamagh…®n oraki, Seba nguibar ekiam…®n aven itima, me iza nguibam ek…®aru. Egha me m…®soghasa nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazim…®n borogh…®n nguazim pozim m…®k…®ra ghuavanadi. Egha me d…®vazim akaright…® a irasava, me temer ekiabar pamten iv…®v…®gha a ginivav…®ra iti.
\v 16 Ez…® amizir n…®ghn…®zir aghuim itim, nguibar ekiar kam…®n ikia kamagh…®n Joap…®n adarazir d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúOi, ia oragh! Ia Joap m…®kemeght…® a iz…®. K…® akam an iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® Joap rogh…®ra izima, amizim an azara, ‚ÄúN…® Joapra?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Joap ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, kar k…®rara.‚Äù
\p Ez…® amizim a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® n…®n ingangarir amizim, k…® akar mam n…®n iti. K…® kamaghsua, n…® bar deraghv…®ra kuarim at…®gh na baragh.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Joap ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, k…® n…®n akam baragham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® amizim kamagh…®n Joap m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe fom…®ra ghaze, n…® os…®mt…®zim ik…®va, Abel…®n nguibar ekiam…®n mang…®. Me Abel…®n zuima, a men os…®mt…®ziba ak…®ri.
\v 19 N…® oragh. En nguibar ekiam a Israel…®n kantrin aven nguibar ekiaba bar dar faraghav…®ra iti. E tintinibar m…®sozir puvat…®gha derav…®ra apiagha, uan arazir aghuibar g…®rara zui. Ez…® n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n nguibar ekiar kam gas…®ghas…®ghasa. N…® bizir tizim bagha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God baghav…®ra itir bizim gas…®ghas…®ghasava ami?‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® Joap kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúBar puvat…®. K…® nguibar kam gas…®ghas…®gh a kuvar…®masa puvat…®.
\v 21 E gumazir vam…®ra iniasa ize, an ziam Seba, a Bikrin otarim. A Efraim…®n anabar m…®ghs…®abar itir gumazim. Gumazir kam, an Atrivim Devit ab…®nasa n…®ghn…®zim gumazibagh an…®di. E kamaghsua, ia Seba e danight…®, e ian nguibar ekiam ategh mangam.‚Äù
\p Ez…® amizim kamagh…®n Joap m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, e gumazir kam m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, e an dapanim fegh, d…®vazim…®n vong…®n a kunight…®, ia dat…®r…®gh…®ram an ganam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, amizim nguibar ekiam…®n ghua uan n…®ghn…®zir aghuim gumazamiziba bar me m…®gei. Ez…® me an n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n ghua, Seban f…®rim atugha an dapanim isa d…®vazim…®n azenan, Joap bagh anekuni. Ez…® Joap s…®gham givima an m…®dorozir gumaziba nguibar ekiam ategha vaghvagha uamategha uan nguibabar zui. Ez…® Joap Atrivim Devit bagha uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghu.
\s1 Devit…®n ingangarir gumazir dapanibar ziaba
\p 
\v 23 Joap dat…®r…®gh…®n Israelian m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanir bar faragha zuim. Ez…® Jehoiadan otarim Benaia, a m…®dorozir gumazir atrivim geghuvibar gumazibar dapanim, kar Keretia ko Peletia.
\v 24 Ez…® Adoniram, a gumazir atrivim uan ingangaribar amuasa inizibar gumazir dapanim. Ez…® Ahilut…®n otarim Jehosafat, a gavman…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazir faragha zuim.
\v 25 Ez…® Seva, an Atrivim Devit amir eghaghanibar ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim. Ez…® Abiatar ko Sadok aning ofa gamir gumazimning.
\v 26 Ez…® Jair…®n adarazir gumazim Ira, a uaghan Devit…®n ofa gamir gumazir mam.
\c 21
\ms1 Devit ko God…®n eghaghaniba
\mr (Sapta 21--24)
\s1 Gibionia Atrivim Sol…®n arazir kuraba ikara
\p 
\v 1 Devit atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, m…®tiriar ekiam oto, ez…® 3plan azenibar dagheba bar puvat…®. Ez…® Devit bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim bagha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azai. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúBizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu. Atrivim Sol Gibeonia m…®soghez…® me ariaghire, ez…® bizir kam bang…®n, os…®mt…®zim Sol…®n ovavir boribar ikiav…®ra iti.‚Äù
\v 2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Devit Gibeonian diaz…® me ize.\f + \fr 21:2 \ft N…® Josua 9:3-15…®n gan.\f* Gibeonia Israelian gumazamiziba puvat…®, me Amoria. Amorian marazi ariaghire, ez…® varazira ikiav…®ra iti. Bar fom…®ra Israelia akar gavgavim ak…®righa ghaze, me Gibeonia gas…®ghas…®ghan kogham. Ez…® Atrivim Sol, a Israelia ko Judabara Israel…®n nguazir kam…®n ikiasa gavgafi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Sol Gibeonia ag…®vasa ingari.
\p 
\v 3 Gibeonia dat…®r…®gh…®n iza Devit batoz…®ma, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® arazir kurar e ia gamizir kam…®n os…®mt…®zim aneg…®vasava ami. Eght…® ia deragh e damus…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azangs…®gh. K…® os…®mt…®zir kam ak…®rs…® ia bagh bizir tizim damuam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Gibeonia kamagh…®n Devit ikara, ‚ÄúOs…®mt…®zir kam, a e ko Sol uan ik…®zim ko iti, ez…® n…® gol ko silvaba e danight…®, bizir kam g…®vaghan kogham. E uaghan Israelian gumazitam m…®soghs…® n…®n azaraghan kogham.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Devit ghaze, ‚ÄúEz…® k…® ia bagh bizir tizim damuasa ia ifonge?‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® me kamagh…®n atrivim…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúSol bar e gas…®ghas…®gh e ag…®vasa n…®ghn…®si, eght…® en gumazitam Israel…®n nguazim…®n ikian kogham.
\v 6 E fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God atrivim…®n ikiasa Sol am…®sefe. Sol…®n nguibam Gibea. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e kamagh…®n n…®n azai, N…® Sol…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazir 7plan e dan…®ngigh. Eght…® e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n me guight…®, me ar…®m…®ghiregham.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Devit me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, k…® me is…® ia dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\v 7 Devit faragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n Sol…®n otarim Jonatan bagha akar gavgavim ak…®ri, egha a dat…®r…®gh…®n a gin…®r…®.\f + \fr 21:7 \ft N…® 1 Samuel 20:14-17 ko 2 Samuel 9:1-7…®n gan.\f* Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Jonatan…®n otarim Mefiboset inizir puvat…®. Mefiboset a Sol…®n igiavotarim, ez…® an a isa Gibeonia gan…®ngizir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 21:8 \xt 1 Samuel 18:19\x*Egha Devit Armoni ko Mefiboset…®n igharazim ini. Aning Sol ko Rispan otarimning, Rispa a Aian guivim, egha a Sol…®n amuir dozir mam. Devit uaghan Sol…®n guivim Merap…®n otarir 5pla ini. Merap…®n pam Adriel, Adriel a Barsilain otarim, a Meholan nguibam…®n gumazim, aning otarir kaba bate.
\p 
\v 9 Devit gumazir kaba isa Gibeonia gan…®ngiz…®ma, me me inigha m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuavanabogha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n 7plan gumazir kaba guiz…®, me bar mogh…®ra ariaghire. Bizir kam, a balin azeniba anima me baliba faraghav…®ra dar aghorasava amir dughiam…®n oto.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® gumazir aremezir kabar pumuning…®n amebam Rispa, a azir inir ghurir maba inigha, m…®ghs…®ar kam…®n ghuavanabo. A inir kabar purirpenir muziarir mam dag…®ar mam gis…®n an ingari. Egha gumazir kabar kuaba iak…®nir mabar dar garav…®ra ikia ghua amozim izir dughiam oto, ez…® amozim arigha gumazir 7plan kabar aghariba rue. Rispa d…®magariba ko aruebar gumazir kuar kaba deraghav…®ra dar gara iti, puvat…®ght…®, kuaraziba ko as…®zir atiaba iz…® dar amegham.
\v 11 Ez…® Devit g…®n Aian guivim Rispa amizir arazir kam baraki.
\v 12 Egha Devit Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n ghua, Jabes…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamiziba bagha ghua, Sol ko an otarim Jonatan…®n aghariba ini. Filistiaba fom…®ra Gilboan m…®ghs…®am…®n Sol ko Jonatan…®n m…®suegha, aning…®n kuamning inigha ghua Betsan…®n nguibar ekiam…®n tuavir akabar aning agura. Ez…® Jabesia g…®n ghua aning…®n kuamning okemegha aning inigha ghu.\f + \fr 21:12 \ft N…® 1 Samuel 31:8-13…®n gan.\f*
\v 13 Ez…® Devit uan ingangarir gumazibav m…®kemez…®, me Sol ko Jonatan…®n aghariba inigha ghue. Me uaghan gumazir 7plan Gibionia guizibar aghariba akufa.
\v 14 Egha me Benjamin…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n Selan nguibar ekiam…®n ghugha, Sol ko Jonatan…®n aghariba isa, Sol…®n afeziam Kis…®n dag…®ar mozim gat…®. Atrivim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n me bizibagh ami. Ez…® arazir kam…®n g…®n, me uan kantri deragh a damuasa God ko m…®geima, a men akaba barasi.
\s1 Israelia Filistiabar gumazir bar dafaba ko m…®sosi
\r (1 Eghaghaniba 20:4-8)
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® m…®dorozim uam Israelia ko Filistiabar tong…®n oto. Ez…® Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghuaghira Filistiaba ko m…®sosi. Me uariv sogha ghua Devit…®n gavgaviba bar g…®vaz…®ma, a ua m…®soghan ibura.
\v 16 Ez…® Filistian gumazir mam an ziam Isbibenop, a gumazir dafabar mam, a Devit m…®sueght…®, an aremeghasa m…®gei. An afuzir igiar m…®zer ruarir me bras…®n ingarizim iti, ez…® an os…®mt…®zim…®n d…®bobonim, 3pla ko akuam…®n kilogrem…®n tu. Egha uaghan m…®dorozir sabar igiar mam iti.
\v 17 \x - \xo 21:17 \xt 1 Atriviba 11:36; Onger Akaba 132:17\x*Ez…® Seruian otarim Abisai, Devit bagha iza an akuragha Filistian kam m…®soghez…®ma an areme. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba akar gavgavim Devit m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE mang…® m…®soghamin dughiam…®n n…® e ko mangan kogham. N…® mati lam…®n angazangarir Israelia e gan…®dim, n…® lam…®n kam damight…®, a mungeghan mark…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Egha Israelia g…®n ua Filistiaba ko m…®sosi. Dughiar kam…®n me Gop…®n nguibam…®n uariv sosi. Ez…® Israelian mav, a Husan nguibam…®n gumazim, an ziam Sibekai, a Filistian gumazir dafar mam m…®soghez…® an areme, an ziam Sap.
\p 
\v 19 Dughiar igharazir mam…®n, Israelia ua Filistiaba ko Gop…®n nguibam…®n uariv sosi. Ez…® Betlehem…®n gumazim Jareoregim, an otarim Elhanan, a Get…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazim, a Goliat…®n igharazim m…®soghez…®ma an areme. Goliat…®n afuzir m…®siam bar ekevegha mati me iniba nuavir masin…®n tretbar suizir aghorir bar dafam.
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® g…®n m…®dorozir igharazir mam ua Get…®n nguibar ekiam…®n oto. Gumazir bar dafabar ovavir borir mam uaghan iti, egha a gumazir ruarir dafam. Ez…® an dafarimning vaghvagha 6plan dafarir puziba iti, ez…® an dagarimning uaghan kamagh…®ra 6plan dagarir puziba iti. Da bar mogh…®ra 24plan puziba.
\v 21 Gumazir kam d…®bovir akabar Israelia m…®g…®av iti, Devit…®n aveghbuam Sama, an otarim Jonatan a m…®soghez…®, an areme.
\p 
\v 22 Filistian 4plan gumazir kaba, me gumazir bar dafar Get…®n nguibar ekiam…®n izezibar ovavir boriba. Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire.
\c 22
\s1 Devit Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha // ighiam bange
\r (Onger Akaba 18)
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Devit…®n apanim Sol ko apanir igharaziba da uam a ini. Ez…® a bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ighiar kam bange.
\v 2 Ighiar kam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba kamak…®n:
\b
\q1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a nan d…®vazir bar gavgavim…®n m…®n iti.
