\v 41 N…® nan apanibagh amiz…®,
\q2 me ak…®ribagh ighegha, na gasegha uam are.
\q2 Gumazir na gifongezir puvat…®ziba, k…® bar me gas…®ghas…®ki.
\q1 
\v 42 Gumazir kaba, uarir akurvaghasa diava arai, ez…® men akurvaghamin gumaziba puvat…®.
\q2 Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n diava arai, ez…® a men d…®mdiaba barazir puvat…®.
\q1 
\v 43 K…® bar me gas…®ghas…®ghiz…®,
\q2 me mati am…®nim nguazir m…®nemeniam giveragha ghu.
\q1 K…® me d…®kab…®ra me ab…®ni,
\q2 mati k…® tuavim…®n
\q3 nguazir beghneaziba d…®ka zui.
