\q2 N…® na gamiz…®, k…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar dapanim…®n oto.
\q2 Gumazamizir k…® fozir puvat…®ziba, n…® men kantriba na gan…®ngiz…®, k…® dagh ativagha men gari.
