\c 23
\s1 Devit…®n akar abuananaba
\p 
\v 1 Kar Devit…®n akar abuananaba:
\b
\q1 K…® Jesin otarim Devit, kar k…® m…®geir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba.
\q2 K…® gumazir, Jekop…®n God atrivim…®n ikiasa na m…®sevezim.
\q1 God gumazamizibar damazim…®n ziar ekiam na gan…®ngi.
\q2 Ez…® k…® ighiar aghuir av…®riba osirigha Israelia gan…®ngi, ez…® me bar dagh ifuegha da bange.
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Duam ia m…®k…®masa, akaba isa nan akam gat…®.
\q2 Guizbang…®ra, God uab…® uan akaba isa na gan…®ngiz…®, k…® dar gun ia m…®gei.
\q1 
\v 3 Israelia en God, a mati dag…®ar ekiar e modim,
\q2 a kamagh…®n na m…®gei,
\q1 ‚ÄúAtrivim God…®n apengan ik…®va, guiz…®n araziba ko God…®n atiatim sara
\q2 gumazamizibagh eghuv men gan.
\q1 
\v 4 A kamagh…®n amua mati, aruem m…®zaraghara ghuariaba puvat…®zir overiam…®n anaga isira,
\q2 mati amozir av…®rim grazibagh izez…®ma,
\q3 aruem…®n angazangarim dagh isiraz…® da taghtasi.‚Äù\f + \fr 23:4 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\b
\q1 
\v 5 God na ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavir mam ak…®ra ghaze,
\q2 A nan ik…®zim damight…® me ik…® gavgavigham,
\q3 eght…® a na ko d…®k…®r…®zir akar kam otevk…®nighan kogham.
\q1 Eght…® akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavir kam, a zurara kamagh…®ra ikiam.
\q2 Bizir k…® ifongeziba, God nan akuraght…® da deraghv…®ram otivam.
\q1 
\v 6 Gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba, me mati benir d…®konir ataghatariba, gumaziba da makuri.
\q2 Eght…® gumazamiziba uan dafaribar dar suighan kogham.
\q1 
\v 7 Gumazitam benir d…®konir kaba batueghs…®, an ain…®n otevitam o afuziv siatam…®n da itir danganimra da akuvagh
\q2 dar apongt…®, da isi bar g…®fagh.
\s1 M…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir // ziaba itibar ziaba
\r (1 Eghaghaniba 11:10-47)
\p 
\v 8 Devit…®n m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavibar ziabar kara. Men faraghav…®ra itim, Josep Basebet, a Takemon…®n adarazir gumazim. A 3plan m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir kabar mav, egha a men faragha zui. A dughiar mam…®n afuzim…®n suiragha\f + \fr 23:8 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 800plan apaniba ko m…®sogha bar me m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire.
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Dodon otarim Eleasar, a m…®dorozir gumazir ziar ekiaba itir 3plan kabar namba 2…®n gumazim. A Ahohin adarazir gumazim. Dughiar mam…®n an Atrivim Devit ko Pasdamim…®n nguibam…®n itima, Filistiaba m…®soghasa uari akufi. Ez…® Filistiaba izir dughiam…®n, Israelia men atiatigha ua uari am…®k…®r…®vegha are. Danganir kam…®n balin azenir mam iti.
\v 10 Ez…® Eleasar uab…®ra tugha gavgavigha, Filistiabav sozi me ariaghiri. Ez…® an aghariba a girima, a m…®dorozir sabam…®n suiraz…® an an ikia gavgavigha mamagh…®ra iti. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God dughiar kam…®n bar Filistiaba ag…®fa. Ez…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba uamategha iza gari Eleasar uab…®ra iti, ez…® Filistian m…®dorozir gumazibar kuabar, korotiaba suamin ingangarimra iti.
\p 
\v 11 An g…®rara itim, Agin otarim Sama, a Harar…®n nguibam…®n gumazim. A namba 3…®n m…®dorozir gumazir ziam itim. Dughiar mam…®n Filistiaba iza Lehin nguibam…®n iza, nguezir azenir ekiam…®n borogh…®n uari akufa. Ez…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir igharazir maba men ganigha are.
\v 12 Ez…® Sama atiatir puvat…®gha tugha gavgavigha, nguezir azenir kam geghuva, a bagha Filistiabav soghez…® me ariaghire. Dughiar kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar Filistiaba ab…®ni.
\p 
\v 13 Devit…®n m…®dorozir gumazir dapanibar tong…®n, marazi men faragha zui. Gumazamiziba ziar kam me gat…®, Devit…®n M…®dorozir Gumazir Gavgavir 30pla. Dughiar mam…®n, azenir igiabar dagheba asir dughiam izima, Devit…®n M…®dorozir Gumazir Gavgavir 30plan tong…®n, gumazir 3pla d…®kavigha, Devit bagha ghua Adulam…®n dag…®ar torim…®n\f + \fr 23:13 \ft N…® 1 Samuel 22:1…®n gan.\f* a bato. Ez…® Filistiaba uaghan dughiar kamran iza Refaim…®n danganir zarim…®n uari bagha averpenibar ingarigha iti.
\v 14 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Devit uan mogomer danganir gavgavim…®n iti, ez…® Filistiabar m…®dorozir gumaziba Betlehem…®n nguibam inigha g…®fa.
\v 15 Ez…® Devit kuarim an p…®rima, a pamtem n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúMaia, tina mang…® na bagh Betlehem…®n nguibam…®n d…®vazir tiar akam…®n borogh…®n itir mozir d…®pam, an tam, tuigh iz…® na danigham!‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir 3plan kaba, me kamagh…®n oregha ghua, Filistiaba itir danganim…®n me ko m…®sogha me abigha ghu. Egha Betlehem…®n nguibam av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n itiar akam…®n borogh…®n ghua d…®pam tuigha Devit bagha a inigha uamategha ize. Ez…® Devit d…®par kam amezir puvat…®, a d…®pam ofan m…®n a isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God gan…®ga, nguzim…®n a inge.
\v 17 Egha Devit kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gumazir d…®par kam tuasa ghueziba me bar atam ariaghiregha ua ize. K…® d…®par kam am…® mati, k…® men ghuzim api. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® anemeghan kogham.‚Äù Egha Devit d…®pam amezir puvat…®.
\p Kar bizir mam m…®dorozir gumazir 3plan kaba a gami.
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Abisai 30plan m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavibar faragha zuir gumazim.\f + \fr 23:18 \ft Gumazir maba ghaze, namban kam a 30 puvat…®. Me ghaze, a ti 3plan gumazibav gei.\f* An aveghbuam Joap, ez…® aning…®n amebam Seruia. Dughiar mam…®n Abisai uan afuzim inigha 300plan apanibav soghez…® me bar ariaghire. Kamagh…®n, a uaghan m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir 3plan kaba ko ziar ekiam iti.
\v 19 Egha a 3plan m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir kabagh itagha ziar ekiam ikia, egha men gumazir dapanim…®n oto. Egha a uab…® 3plan m…®dorozir gumazir kaba ko magh ghuzir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® Jehoiadan otarim Benaia, a Kapsel…®n nguibam…®n gumazim, a uaghan m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir mam. Egha m…®dorozir av…®rir mabagh amua apaniba ab…®ni. Dughiar mam…®n, Benaia Moap…®n kantrin gumazim, Ariel, an otarir pumuning m…®soghez…® aning areme. Ez…® g…®n dughiar orangt…®zim…®n, ais…®n of…®ziba irima, a mozir mam giraghugha laion…®n mam m…®soghez…®ma an areme.
\v 21 Egha dughiar igharazir mam…®n, a Isipian gumazir ganganir aghuir mam…®n m…®soghez…®ma an areme. Gumazir kam afuzim…®n suiraghav iti, ez…® Benaia ter ararir os…®mt…®zir mam inigha an borogh…®n ghugha an a m…®suegha, an dafarim…®n an afuzim am…®kegha afuzir kam…®n a b…®raz…®, an areme.
\v 22 Jehoiadan otarim Benaia, amizir bizir ekiar kabanang a p…®rafaz…®, a uaghan m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir 3plan kaba ko ziar ekiam iti.
\v 23 An ziar ekiam, 30plan m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir kabagh afira, egha m…®dorozir gumazir 3plan ziar ekiaba itir kaba ko magh ghuzir puvat…®. Ez…® Devit uab…® geghuv uab…®n ganamin gumazibar dapanim…®n anet…®.
\p 
