\b
\m M…®dorozir gumazir kabar d…®bobonim 37…®n tu.
\c 24
\s1 Devit gumazamiziba medi
\r (1 Eghaghaniba 21:1-27)
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar mam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua Israelian atara, os…®mt…®zim me dan…®ngasa n…®ghn…®zim Devit gan…®ngi. Egha a Devit m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® Israelia ko Judabar gumazamiziba mengegh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® Atrivim Devit kamagh…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim Joap m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapaniba inigh, ia mang…® Israelian gumazamiziba bar me mengegh. Ia Israelian anababa bar dar mang…®, not…®n amadaghan Dan…®n nguibar ekiam ikegh, mang…® saut…®n amadaghan Berseban nguibar ekiam…®n otogh, n…® gumazamiziba bar me mengegh. K…® e uan gumazamizibar d…®bobonim g…®foghasa.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® Joap kamagh…®n atrivim ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, k…® kamagh ifonge, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a n…®n God, a gumazamizibar d…®bobonim damight…® a bar ghuavanabogh, egh bar av…®rasemegham. K…® ghaze, bizir kam ti, dughiar n…® ikiav…®ra itim…®n otoght…®, n…® uab…® uan damazim…®n an ganam. Ez…® atrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, ga uaning, gumazamiziba mengamin ingangarim, kar en ingangarim puvat…®. Ez…® n…® tizimsua arazir kurar kam damuasava ami?‚Äù\f + \fr 24:3 \ft E fozir puvat…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God manmaghsua dughiar kam…®n Israelian atari. (N…® ves 1…®n gan.) Egha uaghan, ak…®nafarir kam deragha e m…®geir puvat…®, gumaziba medir arazir kam, manmaghsua God…®n damazim…®n ‚ÄúArazir kuram.‚Äù Gumazir maba ghaze, God uab…®ra gumazamizibar d…®bobonim g…®fogh. Kamagh…®n Joap ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazamiziba mengamin ingangarim, kar en ingangarim puvat…®.‚Äù Ez…® guizbang…®ra, God dughiar mabar gumazamiziba mengasa Israelia m…®gei. Egha God men ziaba iniasa me m…®gei, a uaghan dag…®aba a dan…®ngasa m…®keme, eght…® ar…®mariar ekiam me inighan kogham. (N…® Ua Me Ini 30:11-12…®n gan.) N…®ghn…®zir igharazim kamak…®n. Devit kamagh…®n ifonge, a uan m…®dorozir gumazibar amight…® me bar av…®rasemegham, kamagh…®n amiz…® a gumaziba menge. (N…® ves 9…®n gan.) Guizbang…®ra, bar fom…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®g…®a ghaze, A uab…® m…®dorozim…®n men akuragham, egh me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan kogham, Men m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rim me damut…® me apanibagh afiragham. (N…® Gumazir Dapaniba 7:2-7…®n gan.) Bizir kam bang…®n, arazir Devit amizir kam derazir puvat…®.\f*
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® atrivim kamaghsua gavgavigha ghaze, Joap uan m…®dorozir gumazir dapaniba ko me an akam…®n g…®n mangam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me atrivim ategha ghua Israelian gumazamiziba mengasa ghue.
\p 
\v 5 Me Jordan…®n Fanem giregha vong…®n ghuegha, Aroer…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n saut…®n amadaghan ghu. Nguibar kam Gat…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n danganir zarim…®n t…®zim…®n iti. Egha me nguibar kam…®n saut…®n amadaghan averpenibagh ami. Egha g…®n me Aroer ategha not…®n amadaghan ghua Jaser…®n nguibar ekiam…®n oto.
\v 6 Me g…®n ua Jaser ategha ghua Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n otifi. Egha ghua Tatimhotsin danganim…®n ghu. Me ua danganir kam ategha ghua Dan…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n itir nguibam Jan…®n otogha, vong…®n ghua aruem uaghiri nagh…®n Saidon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n oto.
\v 7 Egha me uamategha saut…®n amadaghan iza, Tair…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otifi, nguibar ekiar kam a d…®vazir gavgavim iti. Egha g…®n me d…®kavigha Tair ategha ghua, Hivia ko Kenanian nguibar ekiaba bar dagh arui. Egha me abuan ghua Judan saut…®n amadaghan otogha, ghua Berseban nguibar ekiam…®n otogha ghua Negev…®n nguazim…®n otifi.
\v 8 Egha me uan kantrin nguibaba bar dagh aruigha g…®vagha uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghu. Men darorir kam…®n ruarim, a 9plan iak…®niba ko 20plan dughiabar ghu.
\v 9 Me ghua otivigha g…®vagha, Joap ghua kamagh…®n me uan darorim…®n gun atrivim geghari, ‚ÄúIsraelia me 800,000…®n gumaziba iti, ez…® me m…®dorozir gumazibar ingangarim damuam. Ez…® Judan gumazibar d…®bobonim a 500,000…®n tu.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 24:10 \xt 1 Samuel 12:13; 13:13\x*Devit bar me mengegha g…®vagha, g…®n an amizir arazir kam bagha navim osemegha kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® bar onganigha m…®dorozir gumaziba menge. K…® arazir kurar kam…®n os…®mt…®zir bar ekiam gami. O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ga uaning, k…® amizir arazir kurar kam, n…® a g…®n amadagh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11-12 Ez…® dughiar kamra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n Devit…®n akaba inigha izir gumazim Gat, a Devit…®n g…®n otivamin bizibar garir gumazim, a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® Devit m…®kemegh, ‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, k…® 3plan tuaviba n…® gan…®di. Eght…® n…® dar tam ginabaght…®, k…® anar…®ra g…®n mang…®va, a is…® n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p Am…®mzaraghan m…®zaraghara Devit osegha d…®kavigha g…®vaz…®,
\v 13 \x - \xo 24:13 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 21:12\x*Gat Devit bagha ghua kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam…®n gun a m…®keme. Egha kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄúN…® 7plan azenibar m…®tiriar ekiam n…®n kantrin otivasa ifonge? O, apaniba iz…® ia m…®sogh ian ag…®nt…®ght…®, ia ar…® mang…® danganir igharazibar 3plan iak…®nibar ikiam? O, ar…®mariar kuratam n…®n kantrin gumazamiziba 3plan aruebar me bativam? N…® bar deraghv…®ra n…®ghnigh uan ifongiam…®n na m…®kemeght…®, k…® uamategh mang…® na amadazir God…®n m…®k…®mam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 24:14 \xt Onger Akaba 51:1; 130:4-7\x*Ez…® Devit bar atiatigha kamagh…®n Gat m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® na m…®geir akar kam, os…®mt…®zir ekiam na gan…®di. K…® fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God a zurara apangkuvir God. Kamagh…®n, a bizir manam damus…® a damu. K…® kamagh…®n aghua, gumazamiziba e gas…®ghas…®gham.‚Äù
